# game/Day 4.rpy:178
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_d2a39151:

    # "The summer's sunlight today is nothing but a high-power laser beam.{w} Just standing outside now could cause your body temperature to rise sharply."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 12)
    "今年夏日的阳光，仿佛一束高能射线。光是站在外面，体温就会不受控制地急速上升，很容易就会晒黑，甚至是被阳光灼伤。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:179
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_65783950:

    # "And if you have a sensitive skin:{w} you for sure, will get a sunburn."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 12)
    "今年夏日的阳光，仿佛一束高能射线。光是站在外面，体温就会不受控制地急速上升，很容易就会晒黑，甚至是被阳光灼伤。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:180
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_9410d31b:

    # "But,{w} I am actually outside now.{w} However,{w} it is very comfortable without giving in to the sunlight."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 16)
    "而我现在，就在屋子外面。但是，我并没有被阳光折服，反而特别舒适。为什么呢？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:181
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_5620e744:

    # "Why?{w} Because I'm on a bus,{w} which is a civilization's advantage!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 20)
    "因为现在正坐在科技文明的利器「公交车」里面！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:186
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_e756a5a2:

    # "I'm on my way to see Torahiko's practice at school."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 25)
    "现在正坐着开往风鸣町的公交车。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:187
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_41a4e41c:

    # "When I was looking through the bus window,{w} I could see the ocean not so far away."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 27)
    "一眼向车外望去，可以看到远处一望无际的海。在海面上反射着那无情烈日释放的阳光，闪闪发亮。十分美丽。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:188
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_c2c08149:

    # "The summer sunshine reflecting on the water surface makes it glitters among the sea waves.{w} So beautiful."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 27)
    "一眼向车外望去，可以看到远处一望无际的海。在海面上反射着那无情烈日释放的阳光，闪闪发亮。十分美丽。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:189
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_66120d00:

    # "It only takes about an hour by bus from Minasato to Fumeicho.{w} And it seems that there is a short walk from the bus stop to Kazenari High School, too."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 31)
    "从水乡村到风鸣町大概要坐一个多小时的公交车。下车后不用走多久，就可以到风鸣高中。还好，有事先问过虎彦该怎么走。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:190
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_e9179c81:

    # "So I guess it was good to ask Torahiko how to get there earlier."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 31)
    "从水乡村到风鸣町大概要坐一个多小时的公交车。下车后不用走多久，就可以到风鸣高中。还好，有事先问过虎彦该怎么走。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:194
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_f6e08403:

    # "Finally,{w} I've arrived at the bus stop."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 37)
    "到站下车的我沿着那长坡走了上去，终于来到了校门口前。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:195
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_8cfde332:

    # "After walking up a long hill,{w} I reached the front of something that looks like a school gate."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 37)
    "到站下车的我沿着那长坡走了上去，终于来到了校门口前。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:196
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_8e290d9c:

    # "Inside,{w} there's a little old building."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 40)
    "看上去好像是一间有点老旧的学校。从外观就能看出是一间乡下的高中。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:197
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_6bc9f21f:

    # "The school appears to be the public high school of this countryside area."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 40)
    "看上去好像是一间有点老旧的学校。从外观就能看出是一间乡下的高中。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:198
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_1f9dcc4e:

    # "Well,{w} I haven't seen many high schools here so far.{w} I continue to proceed to the back of the school building."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 43)
    "虽然我至今为止，也没见过很多学校。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:199
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_224604e3:

    # "Torahiko told me he didn't know whether outsiders are allowed to enter the school,{w} so I'd better try not to be noticed."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 49)
    "「不知道校外的人能不能进学校，所以尽量不要被人发现比较好」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:200
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_d84d797e:

    # "I think what he was afraid of is true."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 54)
    "在学校里，有积极参加社团活动的学生们，还有在为秋天的文化祭做准备的学生们，虽然是暑假，但是个个都充满活力。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:201
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_f5def6c4:

    # "There are still many students who are engaged in club activities,{w} and students who are preparing for the autumn school festival inside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 54)
    "在学校里，有积极参加社团活动的学生们，还有在为秋天的文化祭做准备的学生们，虽然是暑假，但是个个都充满活力。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:202
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_bf0168fd:

    # "Even though it's summer vacation,{w} the school is lively as it is during the terms."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 58)
    "能听见管乐社的练习时的音乐，和棒球社员跑步时喊的口号。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:203
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_f21e65a8:

    # "I can hear the sound of a part-time band practicing,{p}and the shouts of the baseball team members as they running."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 58)
    "能听见管乐社的练习时的音乐，和棒球社员跑步时喊的口号。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:204
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_b295adfa:

    # "When I arrived at the pool behind the school building,{p}it was completely past noon."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 61)
    "然后，我来到学校后面的游泳池这里。现在已经过了正午时间。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:205
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_d76457a3:

    # fn "「Konnichiwa...?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 66)
    fn "「你好，有人吗……？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:206
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_25f189f3:

    # "Even though the entrance of the fence seems to open,{p}I was a bit hesitant to enter so suddenly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 67)
