# game/Day 4.rpy:207
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_a6e28eea:

    # "When I try to asked if there's anyone there,{p}I don't get any respond, either."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 71)
    "但是没有人回应。可能是刚才的声音太小了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:208
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_3ed21d4b:

    # "Probably my voice was a little quiet."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 71)
    "但是没有人回应。可能是刚才的声音太小了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:209
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_0484c67f:

    # fn "「Hello?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 76)
    fn "「请问有人吗——？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:210
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_af57a2b5:

    # "I call out in a slightly louder voice this time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 77)
    "这次试着调高了力度大声地喊到。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:211
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_721820fc:

    # to "「[fn]?{w} I'm in the changing room, come in!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 81)
    to "「是博行吗？我在更衣室里，进来吧」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:212
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_0dd10e32:

    # "After my attempt to raise my voice,{w} I hear Torahiko's reply coming from the room on the left,{p}which is labeled as the changing room."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 82)
    "稍微往里面走一点，左手边有一间写着更衣室的房间里面传来了虎彦的声音。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:213
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_a16ce53f:

    # "I continue on and enter the changing room after getting permission."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 85)
    "获得允许的我就这样走了过去，进了门没关的更衣室里。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:214
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_86558021:

    # fn "「Excuse me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 90)
    fn "「打扰了」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:219
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_d948ddde:

    # to "「I'm over here, [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 95)
    to "「终于来啦！博行！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:220
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_dd6e1eeb:

    # "Oh...!"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 98)
    "一进门，就看到穿着泳裤的虎彦坐在更衣室的长椅上。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:224
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_7e3fedb7:

    # "In the changing room,{w} Torahiko wearing a swimsuit is sitting on the bench."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 98)
    "一进门，就看到穿着泳裤的虎彦坐在更衣室的长椅上。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:225
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_0c96d41b:

    # "He looks as cool as the athletes I see on TV with the goggles around his neck and a towel on his shoulders."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 100)
    "脖子上挂着泳镜，肩上披着毛巾的身影，跟经常在电视里直播中看到的运动员相比帅气程度毫不逊色。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:226
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_a3f4f84a:

    # "And I'm also having this feeling inside me,{w} which I guess I only realized after entering the school:{p}I feel relieved to finally have found Torahiko."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 104)
    "刚进校门后只感觉到莫名的陌生感的我，见到虎彦后缓缓地安下心来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:230
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_dd421c35:

    # to "「You're really here, [fn]!{w} Wasn't here\n quite far from Minasato?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 111)
    to "「能来这里辛苦你了！是不是离水乡村很远啊」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:231
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_be22e312:

    # fn "「Well...{w} But I was looking forward too seeing what\n Kazenari High School looks like.{w} And I was going by\n bus, so it wasn't any stressful at all!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 115)
    fn "「对啊。但是挺期待看到风鸣高中的，而且是坐公交车来的啦，不辛苦」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:232
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_6bf349b2:

    # fn "「By the way,{w} aren't there any other swimming\n members or coaches here?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 118)
    fn "「话说回来，其他的社员和教练在哪啊？不在吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:236
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_ec22402b:

    # to "「Actually,{w} today's whole practice has ended in the\n morning.{w} But I asked my coach to let me practice in\n the afternoon.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 124)
    to "「不是啦，只是今天的全体训练在上午就已经结束了。不过我拜托了教练，下午让我一个人在这里训练」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:237
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_fed909c4:

    # to "「Besides,{w} I'm not very busy since there're other\n people to help my dad at home today.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 127)
    to "「反正今天家里那边也不是特别忙」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:238
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_1cd1db14:

    # to "「That's why I'm having a light lunch right now!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 130)
    to "「所以事情就是这样啦，而我现在只是在这里稍微吃个午饭」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:239
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_217e6452:

    # "When I look closely,{w} I see a big wrapped Onigiri in Torahiko's hand.{w} To be honest,{w} that rice ball he's holding must be as big as a bomb."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 131)
    "仔细一看，虎彦的手上有一个被保鲜膜包裹着的特别大的饭团。这就是传说中的炸弹饭团吗！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:240
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_e8e1ac36:

    # fn "「I see.{w} Just as I expected,{w} you're enthusiastic\n about practicing because the tournament is near,\n aren't you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 138)
    fn "「原来是这样啊。真不愧是虎彦，为了比赛还真是努力啊」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:241
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_2f9db7df:

    # fn "「But that Onigiri is definitely not a light lunch\n at all!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 141)
    fn "「还有，这个大的不像话的饭团根本不是稍微吃点的等级啊」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:245
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_0ac75588:

    # to "「Really?{w} I'm not even half full with this.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 145)
    to "「是吗？这个量也就半饱而已啊」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:249
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_2484ab7e:

    # "Speaking of which,{w} professional swimmers on TV burn a huge amount of calories a day."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 148)
    "这么一说，好像电视上说过职业的游泳选手一天要消耗非常多的卡路里，为了弥补那部分的能量，要比一般人多吃好几倍的饭。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:250
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_6505f13c:

    # "So in order to replenish their energy,{w} they often eat many times as much as ordinary people."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 148)
    "这么一说，好像电视上说过职业的游泳选手一天要消耗非常多的卡路里，为了弥补那部分的能量，要比一般人多吃好几倍的饭。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:251
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_85273179:

    # "While I was still busy thinking about that,{p}Torahiko has already finished the rice ball."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 151)
    "正在想这些事的时候，虎彦已经把饭团吃得干干净净了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:255
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_1fd07aed:

    # to "「Well,{w} I guess it's okay to stretch a little before\n the afternoon practice!{w} Let's go to the poolside,\n [fn]!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 158)
    to "「在下午的训练开始前，先做个热身！那我们出去吧！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:256
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_9108af51:

    # "When Torahiko stands up,{w} my eyes just accidentally catch on it..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 159)
    "说完虎彦站了起来，我的两个眼珠子不经意间捕捉到了某样东西……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:260
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_a865d89c:

    # "His...{w} The bulge in Torahiko's crotch..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 162)
    "虎彦的……那稍微鼓起的胯下……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:264
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_ec7b53b3:

    # "Made of a navy blue cloth decorated with white lines,{p}his swimsuit is covering what is so-called his pride."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 164)
    "深蓝色的底色配上白色的线条，所谓行家之间称为「竞赛泳裤」的东西。在泳裤中间可以隐约看到被包裹着向上突起的东西。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:265
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_18527869:

    # "In the center,{w} I can faintly see his thing stored upward."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 164)
    "深蓝色的底色配上白色的线条，所谓行家之间称为「竞赛泳裤」的东西。在泳裤中间可以隐约看到被包裹着向上突起的东西。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:266
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_cba614d4:

    # "The fabric is neither too tight nor sticky,{w} but the wrinkles has emphasized his thing even more.{p}Probably because he was sitting down earlier."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 171)
    "因为刚才是坐着的缘故，现在那个东西更加显眼了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:270
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_1c4029d2:

    # to "「[fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 177)
    to "「喂！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:271
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_7f87c647:

    # fn "「Huh"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 180)
    fn "「哇！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:275
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_8493d425:

    # "Torahiko suddenly calls my name.{w} He makes a such a pitiful sound."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 182)
    "不经意被呼喊到的我吓出了声。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:279
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_3efd1d83:

    # to "「[fn],{w} I know I have such a rare swimsuit,{w} but\n you shouldn't stare at the most important place of a\n man like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 188)
    to "「你这家伙，这泳裤虽然对你来说新奇了点，那也不用一直盯着看吧，还有不要那样凝视男人重要的地方啊」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:280
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_45cd087f:

    # "Torahiko blames me with a terrible look on his face."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 189)
    "被一脸吃惊的虎彦责备……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:281
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_7b541a3f:

    # fn "「Huh?{w} No!!{w} That's not what I meant!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 193)
    fn "「啊，不是，那个，我不是有意的！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:285
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_468599e1:

    # to "「Or...{w} Is it around the age when you are interested\n in other people's things?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 198)
    to "「莫非，博行也到了对别人的东西感兴趣的年纪了吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:289
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_cec0088c:

    # "Torahiko heads toward the poolside while fixing the wrinkles and showing his fangs with a grin.{p}I follow him right after."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 201)
    "虎彦整了整泳裤的同时，一边笑嘻嘻地露出牙齿一边走向泳池旁。而我跟在后面。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:290
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_878baf49:

    # fn "「We're the same age, Torahiko!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 207)
    fn "「你不也是跟我一样的岁数吗！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:291
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_c18aa437:

    # to "「I'm just sayin'!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 210)
    to "「好好好，是是是」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:292
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_b1538fe0:

    # fn "「But --」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 213)
    fn "「可恶……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:293
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_1ef20ee5:

    # "In this situation, whatever I say won't change anything.{w} So I decided to give no more excuses."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 214)
    "在这里再怎么狡辩也是我输了。说什么都徒劳。呜呜呜……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:294
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_b0f9dfa0:

    # "What a shame..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 214)
    "在这里再怎么狡辩也是我输了。说什么都徒劳。呜呜呜……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:303
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_d15f7b3b:

    # "Torahiko, who came to the poolside first, put his towel on the bench and started stretching.{w} I stand on the diving board, look around the whole facility."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 228)
    "走到泳池旁的虎彦把毛巾放在长椅上，并开始热身运动。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:304
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_3e712ca3:

    # "Kazenari High School has a typical 25-meter pool with five lanes.{w} To be honest,{w} I'm a little jealous since there's no pool in the school where I attend."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 232)
    "风鸣高中的泳池是常规的25米长，有5个泳道。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:305
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_57c80c03:

    # "In the meantime,{w} Torahiko is doing some arms stretching and leg movements.{w} But after all...{p}my concentration is still back on his crotch."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 235)
    "因为我现在上的高中没有泳池，所以有点羡慕。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:306
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_466f996e:

    # "Every time his whole body stretches,{w} his thighs shake and his crotch slightly sways.{w} This is..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 241)
    "……不过，我的视线不自觉的集中在虎彦的胯下。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:307
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_39a3b6a0:

    # "Oops,{w} Torahiko will notice.{w} In a moment, I quickly turn my eyes back to the pool."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 249)
    "不好，再这样看下去的话会被虎彦发现的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:308
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_bb63b9e7:

    # to "「Whew, the stretch is complete!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 254)
    to "「热身完毕！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:309
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_6ed06287:

    # to "「Okay, I'm going to swim some 100m.{w} Can you\n measure the time with the stopwatch there for me?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 257)
    to "「等一下我要游好几次100米，"

# game/Day 4.rpy:310
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_341f27d5:

    # fn "「Sure!{w} I'm a professional in measuring swimming\n time, ya know?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 263)
    fn "「包在我身上！游泳的姿势也会帮你检查的」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:314
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_88f40abd:

    # to "「Well then!{w} Prepare to marvel at Torahiko-sama's\n splendid swim!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 267)
    to "「很好！接下来看我虎彦大爷的飒爽泳姿吧！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:315
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_7a261943:

    # "Torahiko, who winks at me, goes to the diving board in the middle lane."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 268)
    "虎彦眨了眨眼，走到了中间泳道的跳水台上。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:319
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_334d320f:

    # "When Torahiko's finally in his position,{w} I give him a signal."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 273)
    "看准时机，等着我的开始的信号。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:320
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_4dd3a8f3:

    # fn "「Ready...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 277)
    fn "「预备！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:321
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_d09d5bad:

    # "At the first signal,{w} Torahiko curls up, grabs the handrail of the diving board and stands still."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 279)
    "双手触碰着跳水台的前端静止不动。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:322
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_4b5d20b5:

    # fn "「GO!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 283)
    fn "「开始！」[虎彦 hide]"

# game/Day 4.rpy:328
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_1409c140:

    # "At the next signal,{w} he jumped into the water vigorously."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 286)
    "在收到下个信号后，虎彦相当有气势地跳入水中。从我按下计时器那一瞬间开始，虎彦那一套连贯的动作，只能用完美来形容。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:329
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_99e56a5b:

    # "The series of Torahiko's actions from the moment I press the button on the stopwatch could only be described as:{w} splendid{w} - just as he said."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 286)
    "在收到下个信号后，虎彦相当有气势地跳入水中。从我按下计时器那一瞬间开始，虎彦那一套连贯的动作，只能用完美来形容。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:330
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_b7d0d7ae:

    # "Torahiko,{w} who scratches the water with a crawl, accelerates rapidly and powerfully while breathing quickly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 290)
    "用着自由泳的虎彦，迅速地换气并渐渐的加大力度快速前进。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:331
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_7e0779ad:

    # "In his stunning swim,{w} there is also the smoothness as he slides on the surface of the water."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 293)
    "那强而有力的泳姿，就像是在水面上毫无阻碍地滑过去一般，游得非常稳。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:332
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_cd76a9f0:

    # "The momentum doesn't slow down after his body turn,{p}as the perfect swim continues until the goal is reached."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 296)
    "在折返之后气势也毫不减弱，直到终点前都是那么完美。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:336
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_eaf28157:

    # fn "「Wow, Torahiko!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 303)
    fn "「好厉害啊，虎彦！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:340
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_fa7aaf2c:

    # "I show the stopwatch screen to Torahiko, who has returned to the diving board from the other side."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 306)
    "回到跳水台的虎彦，看了看计时器上的数字。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:344
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_c0f7ac26:

    # to "「Ah...{w} Well, it's normal.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 312)
    to "「啊……这算普通程度吧」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:345
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_7d451db3:

    # fn "「Eh!?{w} But isn't it so fast?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 315)
    fn "「这算普通！？明明游的那么快，不是吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:346
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_754b5a68:

    # to "「I used to be a little faster,{w} but recently I've\n been feeling in a kind of slump.{w} I still couldn't\n shorten the time.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 320)
    to "「之前的话可以再更快一些的，最近状况实在是有点不好。没什么办法缩短自己的记录」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:347
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_4938fe4c:

    # fn "「I guess...{w} But you're much better than when you\n were a kid, though.{w} Most importantly,{w} your\n swimming performance looks so cool!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 324)
    fn "「是这样啊……但是，跟小时候的虎彦相比进步很多了啊，更重要的是游泳时的虎彦特别帅！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:351
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_7ad78f91:

    # to "「Heh!{w} Well then... I'm still going!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 328)
    to "「嘿嘿！……好了，接着继续吧！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:352
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_d8ddbb64:

    # "After that, Torahiko continues to swim.{w} And each time he does, I'm still the one who measures."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 329)
    "在那之后虎彦继续游着泳，而我负责帮忙计时。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:353
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_52767a07:

    # "From my view,{w} it's not good for Torahiko to swim that far over and over again."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 331)
    "虽然对我来说这已经是一个非常可怕的记录了，但是这种程度肯定是不够的，毕竟接下来的比赛可都是强者云集……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:354
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_570929b4:

    # "But I'm sure that the next tournament will be full of powerful players,{w} so that's why I can do nothing about it."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 331)
    "虽然对我来说这已经是一个非常可怕的记录了，但是这种程度肯定是不够的，毕竟接下来的比赛可都是强者云集……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:361
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_489db91c:

    # "When I noticed,{w} the sun was starting to set a little.{w} I guess it's about time to finish."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 340)
    "回过神时，夕阳的余晖已经照了进来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:362
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_115ad284:

    # "Torahiko changes into his uniform, and then the two of us come out of the pool."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 342)
    "今天就到这吧，虎彦换上制服说道，两人便离开了泳池。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:366
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_4d4a7d45:

    # to "「I need to return the keys to the staff room,{w} so\n please wait for me at the school gate.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 349)
    to "「我要去下老师的办公室还泳池的钥匙，你先去校门口等我吧」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:367
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_cca82374:

    # fn "「Sure, I'll be there.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 352)
    fn "「嗯。等你」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:371
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_df26466c:

    # "I return to the school gate just like when I came in order to avoid any notice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 355)
    "跟来的时候一样，尽量不引人注意地回到了校门口。其他学生也似乎到了离校的时间，与在校门口站着的我擦身而过后就三三两两地回家了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:372
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_22edb447:

    # "Other students also seem to have reached their time to leave,{w} so they're all waiting in front of the school."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 355)
    "跟来的时候一样，尽量不引人注意地回到了校门口。其他学生也似乎到了离校的时间，与在校门口站着的我擦身而过后就三三两两地回家了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:373
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_f2af31dd:

    # "I guess I'll just pass by them on the way.{w} Somehow,{p}it feels like I've become a character in a school movie or so."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 359)
    "总觉得，好像自己成了校园类漫画，动画里的人物似的。居然会在离校时间在校门口等人。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:374
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_acd25b77:

    # "Waiting for someone at the school gate when it's about time to go home..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 359)
    "总觉得，好像自己成了校园类漫画，动画里的人物似的。居然会在离校时间在校门口等人。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:378
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_b6ac4ede:

    # to "「Sorry for keeping you waiting.{w} Here, behind me.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 365)
    to "「久等了。来！你坐后面」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:379
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_b5e03bf7:

    # "Torahiko, who has just returned from the staff room, is riding a bicycle."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 366)
    "从办公室回来的虎彦，骑着自行车来到了我的身边。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:380
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_ce3cdfe2:

    # fn "「Oh?{w} Is that okay?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 370)
    fn "「咦？可以吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:381
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_6fcc50ff:

    # to "「Don't worry.{w} Unlike Tatsuki,{w} I'm the definition\n of safety, you know?{p} It's just a bicycle after all.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 373)
    to "「当然啊。我可跟辰兄不同是安全驾驶的哦。虽然是自行车」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:382
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_0677d238:

    # fn "「I don't know.{w} I'm sure you must have gotten tired\n from swimming that much.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 377)
    fn "「好吧，那就恭敬不如从命啦对不住啊，游了那么久肯定累的不行，还要载着我」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:386
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_16253c3f:

    # to "「I swim everyday,{w} so it's not even a big deal.{p} Here,{w} grab it firmly!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 382)
    to "「我每天都在游泳的啦，这些小事不算什么，体力充足得很。好啦不说这些了，要抓紧哟！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:387
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_f169b2d0:

    # fn "「Wait!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 385)
    fn "「呜哇！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:391
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_f1844c56:

    # "I'm not really accustomed to being carried on a bicycle."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 388)
    "并不习惯被人用自行车载着的我在出发时稍微失去了点平衡，便不自觉的紧紧地抱住了虎彦的腰。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:392
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_b345f771:

    # "That's why when he rode away,{w} I involuntarily hugged Torahiko's waist more tightly than I should have."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 388)
    "并不习惯被人用自行车载着的我在出发时稍微失去了点平衡，便不自觉的紧紧地抱住了虎彦的腰。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:393
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_fc39217e:

    # to "「Heh,{w} you may cling to that feeling then.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 393)
    to "「嘿嘿，就这样抱着吧，我没意见的」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:394
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_e608b60b:

    # "I thought I had to keep a little more distance,{p}but my eyes then were glued to the sight spreading out in front of us."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 394)
    "虽然我想着要稍微离开一点保持下距离什么的，但很快就被眼前的景色牢牢地牵住了目光。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:395
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_3f231d78:

    # "Before my very eyes,{w} the whole ocean dyed in the setting sun magnificently appears below the hill where Kazenari High School is located."
