# game/Day 4.rpy:397
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_1006233f:

    # "The orange sunset wrapping everything is so nostalgic.{p}How sad it must be when this is the day's last masterpiece we see before the night descend."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 4日目.ks (KS 400)
    "跟在公交车上看到的夏日下元气满满的大海截然不同，宛如表情变了似的，被橙红色的夕阳所包裹着给人一种乡愁的感觉，把那夜幕降临之前的哀愁演绎的如此深刻。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:398
translate chinese_simplified torahiko04_8363a717:

