# game/Day 4.rpy:428
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki04_b9e7bba8:

    # "While I was remembering all that,\nI could hear footsteps coming from inside."
    "诶？为什么一想起以前的事情，\n屋子里就传来了笃簌笃簌的脚步声......"

