    fn "「嗯。{p}还以为都是请产地直接送高级食材过来什么的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:829
translate chinese_simplified shin04_06de70fa:

    # si "「We've got so much fresh produce nearby,\n why order in from far away?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「当地就可以买到这些新鲜的食材，\n没必要特地再从远方寄过来吧？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:830
translate chinese_simplified shin04_dc6dd94f:

    # "Has little Shin-kun taken root here?{p}As he said, Minasato is a farming village,\nso who actually would order food deliveries?"
    "似乎被戳到笑点，深君小声地噗嗤了一声。{p}这么说来水乡村也是农村，\n与其说产地直送不如说根本是住在产地吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:831
translate chinese_simplified shin04_a36240c9:

    # fn "「B-but still,\n won't you have to do it for everyone at home?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「不、不过啊，{w=.3}\n这种事平常应该都是家里的人在做吧？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:835
translate chinese_simplified shin04_c50278f5:

    # si "「Everything was all left to someone else back then.\n Still, I'm not a child so I want to be able to\n do some of the everyday tasks by myself.」"
    si "「以前是都请他们做没错啦。{p}不过我也不是小孩了，自己的生活相关的事\n多少会想要自己来试着做做看吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:839
translate chinese_simplified shin04_0d513861:

    # si "「Besides, shopping can be pretty fun.{p} I'm looking for myself, picking something out,{w=.3}\n checking to see if what I want is within budget...」"
    si "「而且，买东西很有趣不是吗？{p}自己去看、{w=.3}自己挑选，{w=.3}\n如何在预算内买齐想要的东西什么的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:840
translate chinese_simplified shin04_9dd71d44:

    # fn "「O-oh...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「咦，啊……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:841
translate chinese_simplified shin04_61cc23b7:

    # "That's so..."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "这个嘛，总觉得感觉还挺"

# game/Day 4.rpy:854
translate chinese_simplified shin04_commoner_84232383:

    # fn "「Shin-kun, you're more like a commoner than I thought.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「深君意外地还挺贴近平民的嘛。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:858
translate chinese_simplified shin04_commoner_c41f47c5:

    # si "「What do you mean by that?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「这是什么意思？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:859
translate chinese_simplified shin04_commoner_18f73803:

    # fn "「I thought you'd be more detached\n from ordinary life or something.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「还以为深君平常的生活会离凡人更远一点的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:863
translate chinese_simplified shin04_commoner_bef95801:

    # si "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:870
translate chinese_simplified shin04_familial_f042f988:

    # fn "「Shin-kun, you're surprisingly familial-minded.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「深君意外地还挺顾家的嘛。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:874
translate chinese_simplified shin04_familial_7d4a1f26:

    # si "「Surprisingly?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「意外？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:875
translate chinese_simplified shin04_familial_cadbf69c:

    # fn "「Yeah.{w} I thought you'd leave\n all the house matters to the servants.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「嗯。{w}还以为家里的事会全都交给管家去办的说。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:879
translate chinese_simplified shin04_familial_1ef86831:

    # si "「...there's only one servant in the house, you know?\n Besides, even I do housework.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「……我家的管家，可只有一个人而已喔？{p}而且，我跟一般人一样也是会做家事的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:892
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_b7cd5314:

    # si "「I don't know what image you have in your head,\n but I don't live a life that cut off from reality.」"
    si "「虽然我不知道你对我有怎样的印象，\n但是我可不是那种活在远离现实的世界的人。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:893
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_bb9affa3:

    # fn "「Ah, yeah.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊，嗯。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:894
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_b2564ac3:

    # "Did I make him mad?"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "该不会有点生气了吧？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:898
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_aaa23f14:

    # si "「I hate it.{p} I hate having people put this image on me like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「我不喜欢这样。{p}用那种方式，凭外表来判断一个人什么的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:899
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_17aafd9c:

    # fn "「Sorry...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「抱歉……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:903
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_165fd015:

    # si "「It's fine...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「不，没事……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:904
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_7e602f22:

    # "Now it kind of feels like the mood's been soured.{p}Afterwards, we exchanged words trying to keep\nthings there, but nothing really perked up."
    "气氛突然变的尴尬了起来。{p}在这之后，虽然为了气氛我试着提了几个话题，\n但都是马上就结束了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:905
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_537d8f51:

    # "The conversation was choppy as\nwe approached the parting of ways.{p}Looks like this is where Shin-kun is leaving."
    "就在这种偶尔零星地交换几句话的情况下，\n我们来到了岔路口。{p}看来得在这里跟深君道别了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:909
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_b3fdc9c3:

    # si "「See you later, [fn].」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    si "「再见，博行。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:910
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_a605d445:

    # fn "「Oh, right. Later.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊，嗯。再见。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:914
translate chinese_simplified shin04_after_2f81be17:

    # "We waved each other off,\nthen went our own separate ways.{p}Hopefully next time we meet he's in a better mood."
    "我们彼此挥了挥手，\n各自走上自己回家的路。{p}下次见面时，深君的心情要是能好起来就好了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:932
translate chinese_simplified shun04_a566f543:

    # "I rustle the hem of my shirt open,\nsending a breeze directly to my bare skin."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "呼啦呼啦地敞开衬衫的下摆，让吹来的风直接接触皮肤。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:933
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e9189c8a:

    # "The steamy air that flows in isn't very effective,\nbut it's better than nothing."
    "不过吹进来的尽是灼热的空气一点用效果都没有啊。\n不过总比没有好一些。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:934
translate chinese_simplified shun04_10a14edd:

    # "It's still morning, and yet the sun's starting\ndash isn't half-done."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "明明还没到中午，太阳的威力还真不是盖的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:935
translate chinese_simplified shun04_2a046a2e:

    # "Surely by afternoon some of the village's\nresidents will have melted."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "中午过后，这个村的住民有些会热到融化吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:936
translate chinese_simplified shun04_851720db:

    # "I'm flowing with sweat.{p}In an impending water shortage,\nmy body sends out an SOS."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "汗不停地流下。{p}由于水分不足，我的身体发出了SOS的信号。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:937
translate chinese_simplified shun04_352203c6:

    # "<SAVE OUR SWEATS.>"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "SAVE OUR SWEATS."

# game/Day 4.rpy:938
translate chinese_simplified shun04_07fcd473:

    # "I'll stop at the candy store\nand buy something to drink."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "去一趟糖果屋，买些什么来喝吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:943
translate chinese_simplified shun04_9eb67089:

    # "Uugh, I'm dizzy just from walking a little bit.{p}I wonder if there's body training to endure heat..."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "唔唔，明明只是走了一小段路，就有点头晕目眩的感觉了。{p}看来要能更耐热的话，就必须去锻炼身体了啊……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:944
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e13d468b:

    # "Gasping for air, I barely manage to make it\nto my destination and its proceeding visitors."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "一边喘气一边走到了目的地，这时候已经有人先到了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:945
translate chinese_simplified shun04_3c59f223:

    # "It's slightly cooler under the edge of the eaves,\nsince it makes shade."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "在屋檐下，有一块因为背阴而稍微凉快的阴影。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:946
translate chinese_simplified shun04_020482dc:

    # "Two people are lined up, sitting on a bench,\nand holding something in their mouths.{p}I recognize them by the shape of their ears."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "两只兽坐在一张长椅上，在吃着些什么。{p}那耳朵的形状看起来很眼熟啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:952
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e9eabaef:

    # fn "「Heeey!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「喂！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:956
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e56cda33:

    # su "「Ah, [fn]-san! Good morning!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「啊，博行桑！早上好！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:960
translate chinese_simplified shun04_38022888:

    # so "「Good mornin'!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「早上好！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:961
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e2c059d7:

    # fn "「Aah, morning, to both of you.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊啊，早上好，你们两个。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:967
translate chinese_simplified shun04_556a7e4e:

    # "I want to greet them,{w} but I'm already\nout of strength to run up to them."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "虽然打招呼是件好事，但是{w}已经完全没有任何体力先到两人那里去了啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:968
translate chinese_simplified shun04_0f85fca7:

    # "I stagger into the store,\nget a bottle of ramune,{p}and finally sit next to Shun-kun."
    "总而言之先摇摇晃晃地走入店内，\n拿了一瓶汽水，{p}接着坐在峻的身边。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:974
translate chinese_simplified shun04_8e9fd259:

    # su "「A-are you alright?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「没、没问题吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:975
translate chinese_simplified shun04_7350fa8b:

    # so "「You were staggerin' around.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「摇摇晃晃的啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:976
translate chinese_simplified shun04_d69ee663:

    # fn "「Ahaha, I'm fine I'm fine.{p} It's a little too hot today...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊哈哈，没问题没问题。{p}只是今天实在是有些热过头了啊……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:982
translate chinese_simplified shun04_70a07f38:

    # "It's different for them.{p}Unlike me, both of them have spent\nmany summers in Minasato."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "他们不一样呢。{p}跟我不一样，两人夏天都是在水乡村度过的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:983
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bcd4c195:

    # "This heat and humidity{p}doesn't seem to be much to them."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "这种炎热和湿气{p}对他们来说似乎不算什么。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:984
translate chinese_simplified shun04_dc0470db:

    # "Rattle.{p}Rattlerattle.{p}Rattlerattlerattle."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "喀拉。{p}喀拉喀拉。{p}喀拉喀拉喀拉。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:985
translate chinese_simplified shun04_162f7601:

    # fn "「Guh, it's hard to drink.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「唔，难饮用啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:986
translate chinese_simplified shun04_4265f803:

    # "I was deceived by it's refreshing\nappearance and made a mistake."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "被那个看上去很清凉的外型给骗了啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:987
translate chinese_simplified shun04_d6bb7111:

    # "The ramune I selected to quench my dried up body\nwas not fit for quickly supplying moisture."
    "为了那干涸的身体所选择的汽水，\n没有办法立刻给身体补给水分啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:988
translate chinese_simplified shun04_d7222536:

    # "Even though I rotate and tilt the bottle many times,\nthe marble is still an obstruction."
    "转了转瓶子，也倒了几次，\n果然是那颗弹珠在碍事啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:992
translate chinese_simplified shun04_c75ab1e7:

    # su "「Um, [fn]-san, there's-」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「那个，博行桑，那个……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:993
translate chinese_simplified shun04_5432da0a:

    # fn "「Wait a minute, Shun-kun.\n I need some carbonic acid.」"
    fn "「稍等一下哦峻君。\n我现在很需要碳酸饮料。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:997
translate chinese_simplified shun04_6c68f615:

    # su "「At the neck of the bottle there's a spot where{p} you trap it and drink.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「在瓶口的那个，要拉开那个扣环才能喝。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:998
translate chinese_simplified shun04_b5fb207e:

    # fn "「What?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「咦？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:999
translate chinese_simplified shun04_fbbdc3f9:

    # "Shun-kun garnishes his words with reservation.{p}Once again I stare at the thing in my hand."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "峻还是很关心的把话说完了。{p}我又重新看了看手中的东西。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1000
translate chinese_simplified shun04_19d9a1a8:

    # "Sexily decorated around the neck of the see-through\nbody, there are a few finger-sized hollow spots."
    "透明的瓶身上的瓶口附近有些花纹，\n是大约指尖大小的凹痕。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1001
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bb8729a9:

    # "In other words, if it does this from the inside,\nthis must be the \"bulge\"!"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "也就是说，把这个拉开就可以了啊！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1002
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e185235a:

    # fn "「Ooh!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「喔喔！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1003
translate chinese_simplified shun04_444667d8:

    # "Gently tilting it, I hold back the marble\nof the root of all evil."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "此时再往口中一倒，万恶的根源的那颗弹珠终于不再碍事。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1004
translate chinese_simplified shun04_aec48e63:

    # "A clear, fresh stream fills the inside of my mouth.{p}My throat dances to the stimulus\nthat pierces through."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "口中满是清爽的水流。{p}碳酸的刺激，在喉咙中跳跃着。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1005
translate chinese_simplified shun04_b1b780ed:

    # fn "「Guh! Thanks, Shun-kun!{p} So this is how you drink ramune.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「呼！谢谢啦峻君！{p}汽水要这样子才能喝啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1009
translate chinese_simplified shun04_46094ae8:

    # so "「You didn't know?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「你不知道吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1010
translate chinese_simplified shun04_04b1e4ca:

    # "There's no implication of criticizing me for\nignorance in his eyes, pure surprise dwells in them."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "那双眼睛并不是在责备着自己的无知，只是单纯的很惊讶。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1011
translate chinese_simplified shun04_97be44da:

    # "Yeah, it's probably common sense\nfor everybody in this village."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "唔，这种事情在这村子里面是常识吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1015
translate chinese_simplified shun04_48b34190:

    # su "「[fn]-san used to drink\n like that back then, too.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「博行在以前也喝过喔。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1019
translate chinese_simplified shun04_524c02a6:

    # su "「You forgot, didn't you?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「忘记了吧？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1020
translate chinese_simplified shun04_1e02fcfe:

    # fn "「Oh, well...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊，是啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1021
translate chinese_simplified shun04_5a1eadb7:

    # "Really?{w=.3} When I was a kid,\nI probably visited this candy store frequently."
    "对了。{w=.3}我在小的时候，\n常常会跑来这一间糖果屋啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1022
translate chinese_simplified shun04_b586026a:

    # "To get marbles at a reasonable price,\nI would often buy ramune.{w} I should have learned\nhow to drink it at some point."
    "因为很想要弹珠的关系，所以很常买弹珠汽水，{w}\n也因为这样子才记得要怎么喝的啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1023
translate chinese_simplified shun04_98d8914c:

    # "Perhaps living in the city, in conjunction\nwith my body that won't lose to the sun,\nhas robbed my memory of the original experience."
    "住在都市里，也许已经把那不畏惧炎热的身体，\n和我在这里的记忆\n一起遗忘掉了也说不定。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1029
translate chinese_simplified shun04_1b07cc6f:

    # "Setting that aside, Shun-kun and Soutarou-kun\nare heartily gulping down their popsicles.\nThey have the same colors."
    "这事先放一边。\n峻和宗太郎正开心地吃着冰棒。\n是同样的颜色。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1030
translate chinese_simplified shun04_d9d58eee:

    # fn "「Both of you are eating the same popsicle?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「你们两个，吃一样的冰吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1036
translate chinese_simplified shun04_91c3932c:

    # so "「Yep.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「是啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1037
translate chinese_simplified shun04_484e9ec6:

    # su "「We split it in half.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「两人各吃一半。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1038
translate chinese_simplified shun04_80a4136a:

    # "He shows me the empty package.{p}Stuck on a stick, are long and narrow lumps of ice,\nthe two of them joined together."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "看了看那空了的包装袋。{p}一份是由两个木棒并排串着的角柱状的冰块。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1039
translate chinese_simplified shun04_93d571cb:

    # "It can be broken vertically and eaten,\na popsicle double bar.{p}It's green and seems to taste like soda."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "可以从中间分成两半来食用。{p}看上去是苏打口味的绿色。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1040
translate chinese_simplified shun04_850cbc9e:

    # fn "「Even so, it's only half.\n What if you both want to eat a whole one?」"
    fn "「不过啊，为什么要分成两份呢。\n一个人吃一份不是很好吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1041
translate chinese_simplified shun04_852e9f04:

    # "They don't have much pocket money do they?{p}I worry about that."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "是因为零用钱的关系吗？{p}还是在担心些什么呢。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1042
translate chinese_simplified shun04_eddca760:

    # "Actually, the way Shun-kun and Soutarou-kun\nare sitting next to each other\nand eating their popsicles,"
    "实际上，峻跟宗太郎坐在一起\n摇着尾巴吃着冰棒的那个样子，"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1043
translate chinese_simplified shun04_880d3b20:

    # "it really doesn't seem\nlike they'd be around the same age as me."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "完全想不到会是跟我差不多同样年纪的啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1044
translate chinese_simplified shun04_5565cc0f:

    # "It gives me the feeling of even smaller\nlittle kids waiting for a meeting."
    "就好像是年纪很小的小孩子\n乖乖地坐在长椅上等待着的感觉啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1045
translate chinese_simplified shun04_99c84751:

    # "Even if the contents of their wallets\nwere 100 yen and 200 yen,\nthey don't feel out of place."
    "所以钱包中只有一个一两百块这种事情，\n一点违和感都没有。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1049
translate chinese_simplified shun04_9b551283:

    # su "「It's too big for me to eat.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「不能一次吃那么多的冰啦。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1050
translate chinese_simplified shun04_8fa0b9da:

    # "Shun-kun feverishly tells me how one\nice cream is too much to eat."
    "峻解释着一份冰棒的量实在是太多了\n不能一次吃那么多的冰。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1051
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e1b3e45a:

    # "Is it because of the smallness of his body?{p}Or maybe he's naturally weak against cold things."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "是因为身体很小的关系吗？{p}还是天生就对冷的东西比较没辙。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1055
translate chinese_simplified shun04_64157948:

    # su "「So when we take it out to eat,\n I choose the small one.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「所以买外面的东西来吃时就选择小的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1056
translate chinese_simplified shun04_48a78d0b:

    # fn "「What about you, Soutarou-kun?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「那宗太郎你呢？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1057
translate chinese_simplified shun04_7bda01ab:

    # "I try to compare their heights.\nThey're not very different."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "两个人以身高来看的话，实在是没什么差异。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1058
translate chinese_simplified shun04_80b5b4c0:

    # "However, I don't think his muscled body,\ncultivated from daily training,\nwould be daunted by something like a popsicle."
    "虽说如此每天用练习所锻炼出来的筋肉质的身体，\n应该不会不能吃冰才对吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1059
translate chinese_simplified shun04_012e3135:

    # "Maybe he went halfsies with Shun-kun\nbecause they're dating?"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "该不会是为了配合峻才吃一半的吧？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1063
translate chinese_simplified shun04_6d709d65:

    # so "「I'm kinda restrictin' myself from too much\n sweet stuff right now.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「我现在必须少吃甜食。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1064
translate chinese_simplified shun04_1a71776a:

    # "When I think about it, he gave me solid reply.{p}But for a growing exercise-enthusiast kid,\nisn't that remark too uncharacteristic?"
    "才刚这么想，就得到了一个相当实际的答案。{p}不过对于一个很喜欢运动而且还是正在发育的人来说，\n应该不会讲出这种话才对啊？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1065
translate chinese_simplified shun04_663b1cad:

    # fn "「Isn't soccer a sport where you run around a lot?{p} I'd think that eating a lot would be helpful.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「足球是一种要奔跑的运动对吧？{p}应该要多吃一些才会有力气吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1069
translate chinese_simplified shun04_0536921a:

    # so "「I'm goin' easy on the sweets so I'll only\n be hungry for breakfast, lunch, and dinner.{p} Having too much sugar is bad.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「肚子饿的话是也会在正餐之外进食，但是糖果不能多吃。{p}摄取糖分太多不好。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1070
translate chinese_simplified shun04_5e895615:

    # fn "「I see.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「这样啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1071
translate chinese_simplified shun04_fe515059:

    # "I'm satisfied with each of their reasons."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "这么讲的话能接受啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1072
translate chinese_simplified shun04_503d0ed7:

    # "They want to eat a popsicle, but a whole one\nis a lot, so they friendlily come\nto an agreement to split it in half."
    "想要吃冰但是一个的分量太多了啊，\n因为同样的理由而两个人感情很好的分半来吃。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1073
translate chinese_simplified shun04_c585fb25:

    # "It's heartwarming."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "还真是愉快啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1074
translate chinese_simplified shun04_df5d6815:

    # "I remove the marble from the top of my ramune\nand check the details of the 2 popsicles\nby intermittently looking to the side."
    "将汽水的瓶盖打开取出弹珠，\n在这有两支冰棒的环境下，\n我向着两人的方向偷看着。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1075
translate chinese_simplified shun04_94ab84fa:

    # "B-but the wolf and lion kids next to me\nhave rod-shaped things in their mouths,\nand they're occasionally swallowing!?"
    "那、那是因为旁边有狼和狮子的小孩子\n正舔着棒状物，偶尔还会有吞咽的动作啊！？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1076
translate chinese_simplified shun04_dfe19a89:

    # "The theme for my research project has been\nstrongly decided!"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "自由研究就决定是这个题目了！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1077
translate chinese_simplified shun04_3672b441:

    # "August 4th."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "８月４日。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1081
translate chinese_simplified shun04_9c7e2730:

    # "Shun-kun chomps little-by-little at the tip,{p}and enjoys rolling the bitten off pieces\naround in his mouth."
    "峻君的吃法是从前端咬碎成小块，{p}再将小块的碎块放到嘴中含着，\n之后再咬碎吞下的类型。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1082
translate chinese_simplified shun04_e3c8f0d0:

    # "He's the type who chews and swallows."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "是咬碎吞下的类型。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1086
translate chinese_simplified shun04_3a316b6e:

    # "For Soutarou-kun,{p}he starts on the upper half of the shaft\nand licks upwards while tasting it."
    "宗太郎君则是，{p}先舔着冰棒的上半部来品尝味道，\n慢慢把冰棒舔成圆锥形的类型。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1087
translate chinese_simplified shun04_4c07d2f0:

    # "He's the type who gradually wears it down."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "是慢慢舔蚀的类型。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1088
translate chinese_simplified shun04_3dc4c083:

    # "They softly bite down, and it changes shape\nin the tip of their muzzles."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "轻轻地把冰棒咬下，再含入口中。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1089
translate chinese_simplified shun04_7701a4a1:

    # "Occasionally they lick up the drops oozing down.{p}Then they put their lips gently around the tips\nand rotate it so that it runs along their tongues."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "不时地舔着快要溶化滴下的冰棒的水滴。{p}沿着嘴唇舔着舌头。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1090
translate chinese_simplified shun04_11868ea9:

    # "Furthermore, both of them are taking their sweet\ntime doing it.{w} This spectacle that will inevitably\nturn dirty spreads out before my eyes."
    "此外对这两个人来说，\n他们一定是再自然不过地做着这些事吧。{w}\n这个不可避免地会变肮脏的光景在我眼前展开。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1091
translate chinese_simplified shun04_c3d3c9bc:

    # "Ooh, it's no use.{p}Dammit, the heat seems to have wrecked\nmy central nervous system."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "唔，不行不行。{p}真是的，因为太热了大脑反应不过来了的样子啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1092
translate chinese_simplified shun04_a3eeafbc:

    # "I withdraw from the immoral direction my thoughts\nwere going."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "得快点跳离那色情的思考方向。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1093
translate chinese_simplified shun04_0d477fbb:

    # "However,{p}my hot bar has begun to raise its head."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "不过。{p}我那发热的棒子已经开始抬起了头。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1094
translate chinese_simplified shun04_aba4f5e8:

    # "I think I should enjoy this situation a little longer!"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "稍微，乐于这种状况不是也不错吗！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1112
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_0b102cef:

    # fn "「Shun-kun.{p} Too much cold stuff isn't good for my stomach,\n I can only eat 1 bite of a popsicle.」"
    fn "「峻君。{p}我也不太能吃过多的冰的食物，\n不过很想吃一口冰棒啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1116
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_87f51db6:

    # su "「Well then, go ahead and have some of mine♪」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「那要吃我的吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1117
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_8a2d65a8:

    # "He offers it to me without hesitation.{p}Not too long, not too thick. The best size."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "峻君毫不犹豫地递出冰棒。{p}是刚刚好的最棒的尺寸。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1118
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_5cbea187:

    # "Half of it has already been chewed,\nand the surface has melted."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "已经有一半左右被吃掉了，表面也有些溶化。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1119
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_1524e9ca:

    # fn "「Thank you!\n Alright, let's eat!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「谢谢啦！那开动了！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1120
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_a6024219:

    # "The heat from Shun-kun's mouth was transmitted\nto the popsicle, but it has already been\nneutralized by the cold."
    "从峻君口中经由冰棒传来的热度，\n中和了冰棒冰冷的感觉。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1121
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_fcfed78d:

    # "This is the rod Shun-kun has been licking\nand rolling his tongue on..."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "这个冰棒是被峻君舔过的呢……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1123
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_318bc1bd:

    # "[fn], bite at it from the side☆{w}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "博行，横着咬了一口☆{w}{nw}"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1125
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_d4d5b9b8:

    # "Kapu. Porori."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "咔卟。嘙咯。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1127
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_83ca79d2:

    # "I bite at the lump of ice I could no longer resist,\nbut I'm too late and it loses its strength."
    "已经被咬过的冰块失去了原有的强度，\n就这样从我的口中逃脱，"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1128
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_3a3e78f9:

    # "My wish that it escapes into my mouth\nalso doesn't come true,{p}and it falls off the stick and onto the ground."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "想要把它含进嘴里的愿望也没能实现，{p}就这样从冰棒棍掉到了地上。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1132
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_8ff30a08:

    # so "「Ah.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1133
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_b7fd84b7:

    # fn "「Ah.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1137
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_8bd97340:

    # su "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1141
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_a847dba0:

    # su "「Fueh.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「唔。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1145
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_3df91c76:

    # su "「It fell off.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「掉下去了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1151
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_b4009bef:

    # "After that, I buy another\nof the same kind of popsicle,"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "当然的在那之后，我买了一支同样的冰棒，"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1152
translate chinese_simplified shun04_biteshun_5d742c33:

    # "Remove a portion of the same length that fell,{p}and, needless to say, give it to Shun-kun."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "分成跟掉下去时一样的长度，{p}当然，递给了峻君。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1165
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_2e13e7ce:

    # "While I'm thinking,\nShun-kun already finishes his popsicle."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "在思考了一下之后，才发现峻君已经把冰棒给吃完了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1166
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_c3526a31:

    # fn "「Soutarou-kun.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「宗太郎君。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1167
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_41504839:

    # fn "「I've also been thinking about my body weight\n from eating too many sweets,\n so I can only have one bite of a popsicle.」"
    fn "「因为要注意体重的关系所以我也不能吃太多甜食，\n不过也想吃一口冰啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1168
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_2f9b517a:

    # "I say with wistful eyes and stare\nat both Soutarou-kun and his popsicle."
    "边这么说边用渴求的眼神，\n交互看着宗太郎的脸与手上的冰棒。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1172
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_66211d64:

    # so "「Um...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「那个……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1173
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_1cfe1c62:

    # so "「Sorry, but no.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「不好意思，不行。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1174
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_f73600cc:

    # "!{w} I've been rejected!{p}But he has an apologetic look on his face!{w=.3}\nPush him further!"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "！{w}被拒绝了！{p}不过表情看上去是有些抱歉的样子！{w=.3}再试一次！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1175
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_b102190e:

    # fn "「Just a little will be fine, won't it?{p} I want to taste it.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「只要一点点就可以喔？{p}只是想尝尝味道。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1176
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_183761d1:

    # so "「No.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「不行。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1177
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_03e5063e:

    # fn "「You don't like me?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「是讨厌我吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1178
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_7ffb453b:

    # so "「Th-that's not it, but.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「不、不是那个意思。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1179
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_1d9abc99:

    # "A brief silence."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "沉默了一下。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1180
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_13c86eb2:

    # so "「...that's like an indirect {size=15}×kiss×,{size=25} isn't it?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「……间接{size=15}接吻{/size}，那个不是很像是吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1181
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_89a69c34:

    # "He quietly mutters.{p}I make up for the part I couldn't hear\nwith the surrounding context."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "那句话讲得非常的小声。{p}听不到的部分已经用前后文推测的方式补起来了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1182
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_62bd5d07:

    # "My midsummer day brain is not to be made light of!"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "要是在盛夏中的大脑被小看了的话是很让人困扰的啊！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1186
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_74c10e7f:

    # su "「?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1187
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_bcb9d0c3:

    # "On the other hand, Shun-kun tilts his head\nin deep interest."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "另一方面，峻君相当感兴趣地歪着头。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1188
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_6c97d67a:

    # su "「I couldn't hear you very well.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「听得不是很清楚啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1192
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_d4a18bcd:

    # so "「Uhh, that's because...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「就、就是，啊……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1193
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_03ded123:

    # "Then Shun-kun stares at him with pure eyes.\nFeeling bewildered,{w} Soutarou-kun's cheeks redden."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "被峻那单纯的眼神一看，宗太郎困惑的红了脸。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1194
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_7505b309:

    # "Shun-kun must still be at an age where he doesn't\nworry about those kinds of things."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "以峻君来说的话，应该是还不会注意到那件事情的年纪吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1195
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_ec5b0761:

    # "My heart is healed by the shy behavior\nof a new friend,{w} and the naiveté\nof my unchanged childhood friend."
    "新朋友那不好意思的行为，{w}\n已经被幼驯染那不曾改变的单纯的心给治愈了啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1199
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_5ad86ce5:

    # su "「Ah, Soutarou-kun!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「啊、宗太郎君！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1200
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_6b27f39e:

    # "Suddenly,\nShun-kun's expression does a complete change."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "峻君的表情突然改变了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1204
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_ba414bc8:

    # so "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    so "「咦？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1208
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_a28c208f:

    # su "「You're a winner! It's the winner mark!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「是中奖喔！是中奖的图案！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1209
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_4ae550c7:

    # "We look at where he's talking about.{p}The popscile Soutarou-kun is licking\nhas become thin."
    "朝着峻君说的方向看去。{p}被宗太郎的舌头舔得已经变薄了的冰棒，\n从冰棒棍透出两个字。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1210
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_1ee9dfc0:

    # "The word \"winner\" is showing through\non the stick."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "冰棒棍上透出了「中奖」这两个字。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1214
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_458846db:

    # so "「It is a winner! I already have one,\n so I'll give it to [fn]-sempai!」"
    so "「中奖了呢！因为还可以再换到一支，\n就给博行前辈吧！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1215
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_1c49c20d:

    # fn "「Oh... okay. Thanks, Soutarou-kun.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊……嗯。谢谢啊，宗太郎君。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1216
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_87e7934c:

    # "Looks like he gave me the slip.{p}I'm heartbroken."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "话题好像巧妙地被扯开了的样子。{p}真失望。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1217
translate chinese_simplified shun04_bitesou_b1db05ea:

    # su "「Good for you!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    su "「真是太好了！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1235
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_bd68ee26:

    # "Smoke rises silently from the pig figurine's nose.{p}I watch it from the corner of my eye,{w=.3}\nas I flop down to go to sleep."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "猪型摆饰的鼻子处正缓缓地冒着烟。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1236
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_e5a0f5b2:

    # "Nothing happens in the country after dinner.{p}It's completely different to the city."
    "晚餐后，我一个人在这种乡下实在没什么事可做。\n不过，这种感觉是在都市的时候绝对不会有的感受。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1237
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_563d47a2:

    # "When I'm there, I have to keep the windows shut\nbecause of the air conditioner."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "因为在都市里时，都会把窗户关紧打开冷气拼命吹。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1238
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_71fa8662:

    # "When I found out my grandpa's house doesn't\neven have a working fan,{p}I was wrapped in a feeling of despair."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "在知道爷爷家没有冷气，甚至连电风扇都坏掉时，我感受到了能够被称为恐怖的绝望感。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1239
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_c6e3b64a:

    # "...When you get used to having it,{w=.3}\nthat's what happens."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "……不过习惯之后，{w=.3}就会觉得这种事就是这样而已了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1240
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_094bf12f:

    # "I tried to come up with an explanation that the low\ntech surroundings somehow lessen the heat,\nwhile fanning myself."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "在以前……也就是科技还不怎么发达的年代，想要消暑，大概也只能像这样用扇子搧风而已吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1241
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_2b38e9e8:

    # "The feeling of a full stomach is making me sleepy.{p}My eyelids gradually get heavier."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "吃饱的感觉自然地变成了想睡。眼皮感觉越来越重了起来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1245
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_ab3ce5cc:

    # "It might be rude to fall asleep after eating,{w=.3}\nBut surely a nap would be okay...?"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "刚吃饱就睡觉好像是有点不太雅观，{w=.3}不过还是先小睡个一下好了……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1251
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_1dc7e36e:

    # "Any chance of a nap is thrown out the window\nwhen loud voices start coming from the television."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "将我那甜美的小小沉眠给打断的，{w=.3}是电视突然发出的巨大声响。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1252
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_419eeeba:

    # "...Come on, I'd finally managed to ignore the heat.{p}As I blearily rub my eyes,\nI glance over at the source of the noise."
    "……到底是怎么了，{w=.3}好不容易才能不去注意天气到底有多炎热的耶。\n我一边揉着眼睛一边看向发出噪音的元凶。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1253
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_85f50d4f:

    # "It looks like a feature on living in the country.{p}What's on screen is fascinating.{w=.3}\nGreen lights are floating freely by a river."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "似乎是介绍如何在乡下生活的特别节目的样子。{p}而画面上特别引人注目的，是那在河边自在地飞舞着的绿色光点。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1254
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_d018d3c4:

    # "The studio audience voices their awe at the scene.{w=.3}\nThat must have been what woke me."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "那个幻想般的景色让观众大声惊呼，{w=.3}因此才把我吵醒了的样子。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1255
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_eb4a547d:

    # "Fireflies, huh...{p}I haven't seen one since I moved away from Minasato.{p}Even then, I barely remember seeing them."
    "萤火虫吗……\n在离开水乡村之后，就一次也没看过了。\n就连当时是怎么看到的，现在也几乎不记得了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1256
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_4da84cb5:

    # "Maybe I should go firefily catching while I'm here.{p}My brain quickly resumes activity as I think."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "偶尔去找找看萤火虫或许也不错。{p}我刚睡醒的脑袋，迅速地开始转动起来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1257
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_c163ade1:

    # "Let's see, where did I last see any?{p}I think I went with my grandpa,{w=.3}\nbut I can't remember clearly."
    "这个，最后一次看到萤火虫的是在哪里啊……\n虽然印象中似乎是爷爷带我去的，{w=.3}\n但现在已经记不太清楚了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1258
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_8660ff02:

    # "...Hmm,{w=.3} It's no use.{p}My memory is like an out-of-focus photograph."
    "……嗯——{w=.3}没办法。{p}脑袋中的记忆，\n已经像是过旧的照片一样变得一片模糊了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1259
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_6d56e3bd:

    # "Well,{w=.3} perhaps I should ask Grandpa where it was?\nI'll need some bug spray, too.{p}Getting covered in insect bites would be awful."
    "哎，{w=.3}地点的问题应该在出发前问问爷爷就好了吧。\n而且还要先弄到防虫喷雾才行。\n我可想到时候被蚊虫叮得全身都是一包一包的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1260
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_c6832e49:

    # "All right,{w=.3} I'm doing something, at least!{p}I start preparing,\nmy chest pounding with excitement."
    "好，{w=.3}不管怎么说先开始行动吧！{p}莫名激动起来的我，就这样东翻西找地\n开始准备了起来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1269
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_6cf18acd:

    # fn "「...This is bad.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「……糟糕了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1270
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_9d31dbeb:

    # "I scratch my cheek as I look around.{p}Getting directions from Grandpa was a good start,{w=.3}\nbut I've completely forgotten Minasato's layout."
    "我抓着自己的脸颊自言自语。\n虽然跟爷爷问了路，有了个还蛮顺利的开始，{w=.3}\n但却因此对水乡村的地形都忘得差不多了而搞不清楚方向。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1271
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_13081198:

    # "As a result, I'm now lost."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "结果，就变成了这样。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1272
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_32deb358:

    # "...I think I know roughly where I am,{w=.3}\nbut it looks like I won't make it to my destination,\nno matter how hard I try."
    "……大致上的方位应该是没有错，{w=.3}\n但是这样下去不管走多久也找不到目的地的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1273
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_1e82f49c:

    # fn "「Aaah,{w=.3} where was it?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊啊啊，{w=.3}到底在哪里啊——」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1274
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_466288b5:

    # "My voice is swallowed up by the darkness."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "我的叫声就像是被黑暗吸收掉一样地消散了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1275
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_8b456ce9:

    # "The lights of faraway houses flicker in the distance,{w=.3}\nthe only other light coming from the moon and stars."
    "虽然远方可以看到有房子的灯光在闪烁，{w=.3}\n但是那个亮度就跟天空中的星星月亮差不多。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1276
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_1c18fb63:

    # "Although it looks brighter than the city,{w=.3}\nthere's still not enough light for me to\nsee where I'm putting my feet."
    "虽然这个亮度比都市能看到的星空还要亮非常多，{w=.3}\n倒是要说能不能照亮脚底下的路的话，\n还是完全不够。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1277
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_f18c6ed3:

    # "What the hell happened to the rustic scenery\nthat I see during the daytime?{p}I regret rushing this far out."
    "在白天看起来很朴素的乡村风景，{w=.3}到底跑到哪里去了呢。\n我开始对于兴致一来就跑出来这件事感到后悔。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1278
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_9b1f3df6:

    # "This calls for a trip back home,{w=.3}\nto get a map from my grandpa..."
    "现在先回家请爷爷画张地图好了，{w=.3}\n虽然有点想这样做……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1279
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_6451fc52:

    # "That said, I feel like I shouldn't\ngo out at a time like this anyway."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "但是，考虑到时间的话，那时候也差不多不该出门了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1280
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_30e8032c:

    # "I guess I could come back tomorrow, but...{p}I've worked up a sweat coming this far,{w=.3}\nand it'd be irritating to return without seeing them."
    "乖乖地回去等明天再来虽然也可以……{p}但是好不容易都来到这了，还流了好多汗，{w=.3}\n实在不想这样什么都没看到就跑回去。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1281
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_0d983677:

    # "I should be in the general area,{w=.3}\nso I'll look around a little longer.{p}I check out my surroundings."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "应该已经差不多到了附近了才对，还是先再找找看好了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1282
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_2d3dfae6:

    # "I can definitely see green lights dancing around.{p}...But, I came all this way to catch fireflies,{w=.3}\nso I want to find a place with many more around."
    "确实在附近草地上是可以看到有绿色光点在飞舞啦。\n……不过，难得特别来看，{w=.3}\n还是想要看看有更大量萤火虫集中的地点。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1288
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_9b78e109:

    # "...Hm?"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "……嗯？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1289
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_74e8785a:

    # "While I was imagining places I'd rather be,{w=.3}\na light clearly different from the fireflies appears.{p}It appears and disappears in a steady rhythm."
    "当我在想着这些不自量力的事情的时候，{w=.3}\n忽然间有个和萤火虫的光芒明显不同的光飞近了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1290
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_f6e8a3a1:

    # "While it does blink,\nit's not weak like the fireflies.{p}It's not green, either."
    "虽然忽明忽灭的，但是很明显比萤火虫明亮。\n而且说起来也不是绿色的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1291
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_4b512dde:

    # "Even from this distance,\nI can distinctly tell that it's white."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "从这里看过去也可以看出是个白色的光芒。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1292
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_73774e1d:

    # "It's moving slowly, but...{w=.3}\nIt looks like it's gradually moving towards me."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "而且虽然速度很慢……{w=.3}但是感觉得出来似乎正在往我这里接近。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1293
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_01953282:

    # "Summer.{w=.3} Near water.{w=.3} A place with light.{w=.3}\nNo other people around.{p}It didn't take me long to guess what it might be."
    "夏天。{w=.3}河边。{w=.3}摇晃着的光芒。{w=.3}没有人的夜晚。\n在去思考它到底是什么之前，直觉就已经有了答案。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1295
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_9bd1c4b1:

    # "No way... Is this thing...{w=.3}{nw} "
    # [旧版翻译]
    "该不会……那个是{w=.3}{nw}"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1297
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_3463b450:

    # extend "A disembodied soul?{p}A cold sweat runs down my back at my guess."
    # [旧版翻译]
    extend "所谓的鬼火？{p}某种讨厌的预感让背上开始冒起冷汗。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1299
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_85bc26e0:

    # "Normally, I wouldn't believe in such things,{w=.3}\nBut in this situation...{p}My mind has gone against my will."
    "虽然我不太相信这回事，{w=.3}但是现在这种状况。\n就算不想也忍不住会想到那些事。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1300
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_490f616e:

    # "I suppress the urge to take off at full tilt,{w=.3}\nand decide to sit down.{p}In times like this, I need to stay calm."
    "我克制住想要马上转身逃跑的冲动，{w=.3}\n更加仔细地观察着它的动静。\n这种时候更是要冷静、沉着地行动才行。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1301
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_94a375f9:

    # "No pushing,{w=.3} no running,{w=.3} no talking.{p}Surely the things I learned from earthquake drills\nin school will be useful."
    "不要推挤、{w=.3}不要奔跑、{w=.3}不要聊天。\n小学时学校教的避难原则，没想到在这种时候意外地有用。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1302
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_5006f1b2:

    # "...{w} Geh!{p}{nw}"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "……{w}啊！{p}{nw}"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1304
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_10c5500f:

    # extend "As soon as I think such a leisurely thing,{w=.3}\nit came right up to me!"
    # [旧版翻译]
    extend "才只不过想了点事，{w=.3}一下子它就已经几乎到了我身旁了是怎么回事啊！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1305
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_1fe2b652:

    # "Oh God oh God oh God oh God!{p}That was a near miss!{p}Wh-wh-what do I do!?"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "糟糕糟糕糟糕！{p}这样下去，我不就要和那种东西擦身而过了吗！{p}怎怎怎怎怎么办！？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1309
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_23b5857f:

    # "I crouch down and tightly close my eyes.{p}It seems to be true that you freeze when\nyou're truly scared."
    "我当场蹲下把身子缩成一团，{w=.3}害怕地闭紧眼睛。\n当从心底感到害怕的时候，会变成什么都没办法做的状态，似乎真的是这样子。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1310
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_192abd49:

    # "Aah,{w=.3} please don't find me..."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "啊啊，{w=.3}拜托请不要注意到我……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1311
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_365034c3:

    # "...{p}...{p}..."
    "……\n……\n……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1312
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_7661a910:

    # "The sound of the rustling grass suddenly stops.{p}There's definitely something close by...!{p}I swallow my saliva with a loud gulp."
    "踏在草上的声音在我的身旁停了下来。\n就在旁边，{w=.3}确实有某种东西……！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1313
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_365034c3_1:

    # "...{p}...{p}..."
    "……\n……\n……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1314
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_09ac838f:

    # "...Nothing happened?{p}Timidly,{w=.3} I open one eye."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "……什么事都没发生？{p}我满怀恐惧地，{w=.3}张开一只眼睛偷看。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1319
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_8e3daec9:

    # "When I look up,{w=.3}\nI see the freshly-severed head of a bear."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "张开眼看到的是，{w=.3}一个熊的脑袋浮在那里。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1325
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_9ea25908:

    # fn "「Gyaaah!!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「呀啊——！！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1326
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_1eba57d7:

    # "I sink back down to the ground.{p}As I lie there, trembling,{w=.3}\nthe head suddenly speaks."
    "我跌坐在地，整个人吓到浑身发抖。\n没想到，{w=.3}这时那个脑袋却说话了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1327
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_4dcc625c:

    # who "「...Hey,{w=.3} [ln]」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    who "「……喂，{w=.3}西村。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1328
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_56bea375:

    # fn "「N-n-n-no!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「什什什什什什什什什」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1329
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_917afe7e:

    # who "「[ln],{w=.3} it's me.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    who "「西村，{w=.3}是我。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1330
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_04fef897:

    # "Odd that it knows my name.{w=.3}\nI gingerly decide to check it again."
    "正想说鬼怎么会知道自己的名字的我，{w=.3}\n再次害怕地抬起头来确认。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1331
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_e509f519:

    # "I've seen that disembodied head before.{w=.3}\nIn fact, it's a face I know very well..."
    "那个脑袋，我见过……正确来说，{w=.3}\n是根本就很熟悉。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1332
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_cd0b3113:

    # fn "「Wh-{w=.3}what the...{w=.3} You aren't Juuichi-san, are you?{p} Please don't scare me...」"
    fn "「什、{w=.3}什么嘛……{w=.3}原来是柔一啊。\n拜托不要吓我啦……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1337
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_de843109:

    # ju "「...That's not what I was doing.{p} I just came from over there.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「……就算你这么说。{p}我也只是单纯地往你这里走过来而已啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1338
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_b5ad05af:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「咦。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1342
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_d852785e:

    # ju "「I could see you by the river,{w=.3} and came to warn you.{p} It's dangerous to be near the water without a light.」"
    ju "「远远就可以看到你一个人站在河边。{p}在这么暗的地方，{w=.3}却连灯都没有拿，\n离水边又那么近，我想说很危险，所以才过来看看。」"

