    fn "「……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1348
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_c21cb17d:

    # "So it was all a complete misunderstanding?{p}The light I thought was a soul is just a flashlight?{w=.3}\nThe presence I felt so close to me was Juuichi-san?"
