    fn "「真的很对不起！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1355
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_d4ae7052:

    # "I threw myself prostrate on the ground,\nand apologized to Juuichi-san."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "我用马上要跪地拜倒的气势跟柔一道了歉。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1366
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_23ee1877:

    # ju "「So,{w=.3} you thought I was a ghost?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「也就是说，{w=.3}你把我当成是幽灵了吗。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1367
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_8e9466a0:

    # fn "「Yeah...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「是的……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1368
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_2183f98f:

    # "As I finish explaining why I was screaming,{w=.3}\nJuuichi-san sighs deeply."
    "在我说明为什么会突然发出惨叫声之后，{w=.3}\n柔一深深地叹了口气。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1372
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_adeda287:

    # ju "「...I've been told my bluntness is scary,{w=.3}\n but this is the first time I've been\n mistaken for another creature entirely.」"
    ju "「……虽然常常被说面无表情的样子很恐怖，{w=.3}\n但被当成生物以外的东西还是第一次。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1373
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_bdf73f62:

    # "I-I might have been mistaken,\nbut I was really scared!"
    "虽、{w=.3}虽然确实弄错了是我自己的问题没错，\n但我可是真的很害怕的啊！"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1377
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_d8ea6845:

    # ju "「You shouldn't be in a place\n like this without a light.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「是没有拿灯就跑到这么暗的地方的你的错。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1378
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_25404953:

    # "My protesting is cut short in an instant.{p}...Yes,{w=.3} I completely agree."
    "微弱的抗议一瞬间就被打碎了。\n……是，{w=.3}完全就是那样没错。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1379
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_5c2b51e3:

    # "That reminds me,{w=.3} didn't Grandpa tell me\nto take a flashlight with me?{p}I ended up leaving it behind, though."
    "说起来，{w=.3}出门前爷爷有说过要记得带手电筒的。\n后来因为不想要手上拿东西而就放着没带了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1380
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_b143253a:

    # "Don't tell me that's what caused all this...{p}Is this what 'the future is a closed book' means?"
