    "结果因此造成了这样子的结果……{p}只能说真的是世事难料啊，{w=.3}这个。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1395
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_1196e453:

    # boy "「Juuichi is bothered by all this.{w=.3}\n Don't you think that you\n shouldn't say things like that, [fn]?」"
    boy "「那种话柔一听了会很在意的，{w=.3}\n可不能再那么说喔，博行？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1396
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_251cf341:

    # fn "「Ooh,{w=.3} I'm so ashamed of myself...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「呜呜呜，{w=.3}没脸见人了……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1400
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_b5d0a4aa:

    # ju "「Wait a minute.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「等一下。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1404
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_e5700345:

    # "Juuichi-san looks towards us with sharp eyes."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "柔一像是想到什么似的，朝我们投过来锐利的眼神。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1408
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_89bf4a87:

    # ju "「I may have a somewhat scary face,{w=.3}\n but I don't remember saying that it bothers me.」"
    ju "「这样讲可能有点强势，{w=.3}\n但是我怎么不记得我说过会在意这种事情之类的话。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1409
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_06cb3050:

    # boy "「Hm? It doesn't?{w} Just the other day,\n you crossed paths with an elementary school student.{p} You looked awfully sad as he ran away crying.」"
    boy "「咦，不是吗？{w}记得在不久前在路上遇到过小学生，\n结果让他吓哭了不是吗。\n看着那孩子逃走的柔一，{w=.3}\n脸上的表情明明就是很寂寞的样子——」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1410
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_6cb51257:

    # boy "「But,{w=.3} if you say I'm wrong,\n then I must be wrong, right?」"
    boy "「不过，{w=.3}柔一说不是那样的话，\n可能就是我弄错了吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1414
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_90bf51ab:

    # ju "「...How did you see that?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「……到底是在哪看见的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1418
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_7c7a2aaf:

    # boy "「Hehehe,{w=.3} it's a secret.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    boy "「呼呼呼，{w=.3}秘密——」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1419
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_c20597ac:

    # "As he smiles,{w=.3}\nJuuichi-san has no choice but to stay silent.{p}Instead, {w=.3}{nw}"
    "看到那个软绵绵的笑容，{w=.3}\n就连柔一也说不出话来的样子。\n相对地，柔一倒是重重地哼了一声。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1421
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_aa3ecc63:

    # extend "he sighs heavily."
    # [旧版翻译]
    extend "柔一深深地叹了口气。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1425
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_3712c9d5:

    # boy "「Seems like that kid had gotten lost.{p} It was bad enough that he was alone and scared,{w=.3}\n but then a scary old man started talking to him.」"
    boy "「看来似乎是迷路了的样子呢，那孩子。{p}这时候通常会既害怕又不安吧，{w=.3}\n突然被不认识的恐怖叔叔搭话，会那样也没办法。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1426
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_6e399740:

    # boy "「So,{w=.3} you've been putting up with it so far.\n But you're getting tired of it, right?」"
    boy "「肯定是，{w=.3}一直在忍耐着的恐怖感\n因此整个爆发出来了吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1430
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_3a33bb74:

    # ju "「Old man...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「叔叔……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1431
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_fb2bd3de:

    # "That was a mean thing to say to Juuichi-san.{p}But, from the eyes of a child,{w=.3}\nMaybe a high school student would look old?"
    "这句话对柔一来说还真是残酷啊。\n不过对那个年龄的小孩子来说，{w=.3}\n高中生可能也算是大人的一部分也不一定。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1432
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_5cca9454:

    # ju "「[ln],{w=.3} are you going to back me up here?」"
