translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_319b93fb:

    # "He smiles, softly.{p}I can't seem to look away from him.\nIt's like I'm being held in a vice."
    "他脸上的微笑真的是非常柔和。\n但是，{w=.3}简直就像是被某种力量给箝住一般，\n完全没办法从他身上移开视线。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1450
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_749d0f2e:

    # fn "「Na,{w=.3} na...」"
