    # ju "「I'll give you a ride home.{w=.3}\n Hurry up and get on.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「我把你送回家，{w=.3}快点上来。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1497
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_38187fde:

    # fn "「What?!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「咦咦？！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1498
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_838b338a:

    # "I blurt out my response a bit too loudly\nat his sudden proposal."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "对这个突然的要求，我想都没想就发出了惊人的喊声。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1499
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_e17a0a78:

    # fn "「You don't need to do that!{p} Give me a minute and I'll be able to stand.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「不能那么麻烦你啦！{p}稍微休息一下就可以站起来了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1500
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_0bbfd796:

    # ju "「There's no way I'm going to\n leave you here in the dark.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「不可能把你一个人丢在这这么暗的地方吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1501
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_81e1d6c9:

    # fn "「Yeah, but...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「虽然可能是那样啦……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1502
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_cbf9afba:

    # ju "「Then don't just sit there and whine.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「那就不要再说什么任性的话了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1503
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_da733c5f:

    # fn "「...Sorry,{w=.3} I'll do it.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「……抱歉。{w=.3}那就麻烦你了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1504
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_fe45a1ee:

    # "I eventually give in.{p}With a word of thanks,{w=.3}{nw}"
    "结果我还是妥协了。\n一边跟柔一道谢，{w=.3}{nw}"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1506
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_e4fc9ee3:

    # extend "\nI entrust my body to Juuichi-san's back."
    # [旧版翻译]
    extend "一边让自己的身体靠到了柔一的背上。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1508
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_fb53e5b9:

    # "I can feel him tensing up.{p}Without any time to think,\nI'm hoisted off the ground."
    "可以感觉到柔一的身体开始出力。\n一瞬间，我的身体就被柔一简单地从地上被背了起来。\n为了怕掉下去，我连忙抱紧柔一的脖子。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1509
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_1f1db24d:

    # "I hastily wrap my arms around his neck,\nso that I don't fall off."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "为了怕掉下去，我连忙抱紧柔一的脖子。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1510
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_8836d6dc:

    # "His short brown fur isn't\nas bristly as I thought it would be.{p}With each step he takes, it tickles my arms a bit."
    "柔一那短短的棕色兽毛，{w=.3}并没有我想像中那么硬。\n每当柔一举步前进时，{w=.3}我的手腕直接碰到兽毛的部分，稍微会有些痒。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1511
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_52e279b8:

    # "I can see the world from 2 metres up.{p}This must be the way Juuichi-san sees the world.{p}The scenery seems to feel fresh, for some reason."
    "二公尺高的地方看到的世界。\n柔一平时看到的，就是像这样的景象吧。\n虽然这种景色对他来说理所当然，{w=.3}但对我而言却很新鲜。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1520
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d93886f7:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san,{w=.3} aren't I heavy?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「柔一，{w=.3}这样不会太重吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1521
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b8d0ec2f:

    # "I ask him quietly, as he carries me in silence."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "看柔一一直沉默地背着我前进，{w=.3}我忍不住问道。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1522
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_85d9c5ff:

    # ju "「The guys I usually throw around are a lot heavier.{p} ...Tora, for instance.」"
    ju "「平常就经常要把更重的人给摔出去了。\n……像是虎那家伙。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1523
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_6b3da311:

    # fn "「Hahaha...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「哈哈哈……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1524
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_e41b38c2:

    # "I let out a dry laugh.{p}Since being back, I've witnessed Torahiko\ngetting thrown more than a few times..."
    "我忍不住发出了有些尴尬的笑声。\n虎彦跑去多管闲事结果被柔一给摔出去的景象，{w=.3}\n确实回来没多久就已经看到过好几次了……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1525
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_00a301a4:

    # "It also feels like Torahiko knows he's going to get\nthrown, and provokes Juuichi-san into doing it."
    "虎彦也是，明明知道会被摔出去，\n却仍然跑去开柔一玩笑。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1526
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_9193e345:

    # ju "「...I don't know why,{w=.3}\n but lately he's been particularly bad.{p} I guess he used to be more endearing.」"
    ju "「……虽然不知道是为什么，{w=.3}\n但那家伙最近特别烦啊。\n以前明明是还挺可爱的家伙的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1527
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_97d4faa4:

    # fn "「Have you guys really changed that much?{p} As soon as you started messing around,{w=.3}\n it was like the old days again.」"
    fn "「有这样的事喔？{p}他总是爱开玩笑这点，{w=.3}\n我印象中好像以前就是这样了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1528
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d28bbb0a:

    # ju "「He used to be more timid about it,{w=.3}\n but lately he doesn't hesitate at all.」"
    ju "「以前还多少会怕我的，{w=.3}\n最近开始变得越来越不在乎了啊。\n……这个，{w=.3}肯定是受到了辰的不良影响没错。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1529
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_4831721b:

    # ju "「...I'm certain that Tatsu-san is\n being a bad influence on him.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「……我肯定是受到了辰的不良影响没错。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1530
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_278908b5:

    # "Juuichi-san sighs deeply.{p}To clear away the heavy mood,{w=.3}\nI hurriedly change the subject."
    "柔一深深地叹了口气。\n为了渐渐变得沉重的气氛给打散，{w=.3}\n我连忙试着转移话题。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1531
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_dfaac953:

    # fn "「Th-that doesn't mean that Torahiko means offense!{p} ...By the way,{w=.3} what were you doing out here\n at this hour?」"
    fn "「那个，{w=.3}虎彦会做那些事也不是有恶意的啦！{p}……说起来，{w=.3}\n柔一在这种时间，是来做什么啊？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1532
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_e217e8f0:

    # "I finally ask the question that's been on my mind.{p}I didn't think anybody in the village would be\naround the riverbed at a time like this..."
    "刚刚就觉得有点困惑，所以还是试着问了。\n就算是当地人，{w=.3}这种时间应该也没有什么事情会需要特地跑到河边去才对……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1533
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_e3593ae6:

    # ju "「...Taking a walk.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「……来散步。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1534
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_abac8d44:

    # fn "「A walk?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「散、{w=.3}散步吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1535
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_5916133e:

    # ju "「Yeah.{w} It's kind of a daily routine for me.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「啊啊。像例行公事那样的。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1536
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d3260a2d:

    # fn "「Wow,{w=.3} really?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「咦，{w=.3}是这样啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1537
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_2e7da5f3:

    # "It feels like I just learned something.{p}I had an image in my head of him being stoic,\nand practicing judo in his spare time."
    "有种突然发现了什么意外的真相的感觉。\n柔一确实，感觉会连私人时间都会拿来练习柔道，\n有那种生活作息非常严格的印象。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1538
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b9de4c67:

    # ju "「What were you doing out there, anyway?{p} What lead to you mistaking me for something else?」"
    ju "「西村你又是为什么会在这的？\n虽然为什么会把我看错的部分已经问过了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1539
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_bf9b36ab:

    # fn "「Didn't I tell you?{p} I was planning on catching fireflies.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「这么说起来我刚刚好像没讲？{p}我是来找萤火虫的，{w=.3}这样。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1540
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_158ca7a5:

    # ju "「Catching fireflies?{p} That's quite tasteful of you.」"
    ju "「找萤火虫啊。\n还挺风雅的嘛，这不是很好吗。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1541
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_0f473176:

    # "He talked with a slightly gentler tone of voice."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "接着，柔一说话的音调突然降低了些。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1542
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_5cc06818:

    # ju "「...If you're looking for fireflies, though,\n I think you should go farther upstream.」"
    ju "「……可是西村，{w=.3}萤火虫比较多的地方，\n应该在更上游才对。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1543
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_7ff40f25:

    # fn "「Huh,{w=.3} that's weird.{p} Grandpa said they'd be around here.」"
    fn "「咦，{w=.3}这可奇怪了。\n照爷爷跟我说的应该在这附近才对呀。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1544
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_7f42e291:

    # "I explain the place Grandpa told me about.{p}Then, Juuichi-san sighs softly."
    "我把爷爷告诉我的地点说明了一下。\n结果，{w=.3}柔一又再次深深叹了口气。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1545
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b071b93f:

    # ju "「...I knew it. You can't remember the area, can you?{p} Even though your grandfather\n told you where to find them?」"
    ju "「……结果根本是你弄错地点了嘛。\n你爷爷可是有好好地把萤火虫群生地告诉你了喔？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1546
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b49ff7a7:

    # fn "「...No comment.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「……对不起，我无从辩驳。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1547
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d52b5496:

    # "Just when I feel like I'm starting to remember,{w=.3}\nI'm reminded by the fact that I don't."
    "虽然之前多少有想过会不会是这样，{w=.3}\n但被这样直接地指出来还是让我大受震惊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1548
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d0b7c4bf:

    # ju "「If you go there now, you'll be up too late.{p} Your body's not up to it, either.{w=.3}\n You should stop for today.」"
    ju "「现在要到那里去的话，会有点太晚。\n你的身体状况也是个问题。{w=.3}今天就先回去比较好。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1549
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_5496e5ac:

    # "The whole cause of this was that I didn't prepare,\nand rushed out as quickly as I could.{p}Well, that and being strangely stubborn."
    "要说起来，{w=.3}也是我没有做什么准备就这样跑出来造成的。\n在奇怪的地方太坚持了的样子。\n我在听了柔一说的话后便乖乖地自我反省起来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1550
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d14fb2c8:

    # "I quietly reflected on Juuichi-san told me."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "我在听了柔一说的话后便乖乖地自我反省起来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1551
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_698f5d35:

    # "Besides,{w=.3} I feel a little embarrassed for\nsaying where I want to go,\ndespite not having a pair of working legs."
    "而且，{w=.3}自己已经是没办法行走的状态了，\n如果还说什么想去那里这种过份任性的话，\n就连我也会觉得实在不太好。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1552
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_c6caaa6e:

    # "It's the same as getting on Juuichi-san's back,{w=.3}\nand telling him where to go."
    "因为那样的话，{w=.3}根本就是在要求\n柔一这样背着我走到目的地的意思嘛。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1553
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_0d7dd700:

    # "I'm sure if I did that,{w=.3}\nhe'd bring the hammer down on me."
    "都已经被柔一骂了，要是还说那种话，{w=.3}\n很可能柔一会因此大发雷霆也不一定。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1554
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_3b02d897:

    # "...I remember what happened to Torahiko,{w=.3}\nand involuntarily shudder."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "……想到虎彦发生过的惨状，{w=.3}我忍不住抖了两下。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1555
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_bc7a0d10:

    # ju "「Hm?{w=.3} Are you cold?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「嗯，{w=.3}觉得冷？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1556
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_448997df:

    # fn "「Oh,{w=.3} no,{w=.3} I'm fine.{p} Your body is warm.」"
    fn "「啊，{w=.3}不是，{w=.3}我没事。\n柔一的身体很温暖，一点都不冷。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1557
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_1952fb49:

    # ju "「...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1558
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_0367a4b4:

    # "Juuichi-san falls silent.{p}Huh?{w=.3} I didn't say anything particularly weird...{p}Did I?"
    "我说完后柔一却沉默了下来。\n咦，{w=.3}我应该没有说什么奇怪的话……吧？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1559
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_01739776:

    # "Thanks to their fur,{w=.3}\nbeastmen trap heat better than humans."
    "因为有兽毛的关系，{w=.3}\n兽人比人类还要容易累积热量。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1560
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_692e3bf2:

    # "In fact,{w=.3} Juuichi-san's body temperature is gradually\nbeing transferred to me through his back."
    "其实，{w=.3}我身体接触到柔一的部分，\n可以感觉到比我的体温还要高的温度正传了过来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1561
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_3c0aa41d:

    # "Still,{w=.3} it doesn't feel strange or uncomfortable.{p}Actually,{w=.3} it makes me feel a\nvaguely familiar sense of relief."
    "不过，{w=.3}很不可思议地却没有觉得不舒服。\n甚至可以说还有一种令人怀念的安心感，{w=.3}\n有这样的感觉。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1562
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_38abb49d:

    # "Under our combined weight,\nthe gravel makes a loud crunching sound."
    "脚下，{w=.3}可以听到柔一承担着两人份的重量的脚步声。\n在这个道路几乎都没有铺设柏油的水乡村，\n这种声音倒是挺常听见的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1563
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_50595ce6:

    # "There aren't many paved roads in Minasato,{w=.3}\nso crunching gravel is not an unusual sound."
    "在这个道路几乎都没有铺设柏油的水乡村，{w=.3}\n这种声音倒是挺常听见的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1567
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_0b40fed3:

    # "The sound is rhythmic.\nI'm being rocked up and down.\nWarmth is coming off Juuichi-san's body."
    "听着这规律的脚步声。\n身体微微上下摇晃着。\n不断传来令人安心的温暖。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1568
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_0edb1e54:

    # "...{p}...{p}...Zzz..."
    "……\n……\n……咚。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1572
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_6cf27555:

    # "Whoa,{w=.3} I dozed off there for a second.{p}I quickly pull back my face that had been buried in\nthe back of Juuichi-san's neck."
    "糟糕，{w=.3}刚刚差点不小心睡着。\n我连忙把埋到柔一的后颈上的脸给抬起来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1573
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_bb0bb979:

    # "Now that I think about it,\nI was falling asleep before I left the house."
    "这么说起来，出门之前也是小睡了一下却被打断。\n不习惯的夜间行走也是很累人，{w=.3}这样下去\n可能真的会睡着也不一定。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1574
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_2344225b:

    # "Walking around in an unfamiliar place\nat night probably didn't help,\nso it's not surprising that I dozed off like that."
    "在不习惯的地方走夜间路应该也是原因之一，{w=.3}\n这一点必须要自我反省才行。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1575
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_16c3d357:

    # "That said,{w=.3}\nit'd be rude to Juuichi-san if I fell asleep."
    "接着，虽然我就像不想从船上掉下去一样地努力集中精神，{w=.3}\n柔一还是转过头来跟我说了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1576
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_3b6f328b:

    # "Oh, did he notice me starting to doze off?{w=.3}\nHe turns his head and talks to me."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "可是不管怎么说，就这样在柔一的背上睡着也未免太失礼了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1577
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b7c8cb0d:

    # ju "「You seem sleepy.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「想睡了吗。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1578
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_63abd9f9:

    # fn "「I-{w=.3}I'm not going to sleep! Not yet...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「没、{w=.3}没有要睡啦，现在还没。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1579
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_403c8930:

    # ju "「...That's basically admitting you're sleepy.{p} I'll wake you up when we reach your house.{w=.3}\n Rest until then.」"
    ju "「……这不就是承认了很想睡了吗。\n到你家附近时我会叫你起来的。{w=.3}在那之前就先睡吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1580
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_4a4c600f:

    # fn "「But,{w=.3} that's...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「可是，{w=.3}这有点……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1581
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_88a92360:

    # ju "「Don't worry.{p} I'm doing this because I want to.」"
    ju "「西村没必要在意这么多。\n这是我自己想这么做的而已。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1582
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_fdd5c6d7:

    # fn "「Ah,{w=.3} I need to tell you how to get to my house...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊，{w=.3}可是，{w=.3}不用带路吗，我家……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1583
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d35053d7:

    # ju "「I've lived here for a long time.{p} ...There's no reason for me to have forgotten.」"
    ju "「我可是一直住在这里的人。\n……不可能连这种事也忘了吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1584
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_1a925554:

    # fn "「...Sorry.{w=.3}\n I guess I'll sleep for a bit.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「……抱歉。{w=.3}那，{w=.3}我小睡一下。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1585
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_2a9dd5de:

    # "During this short exchange,{w=.3}\ndrowsiness attacks me without mercy."
    "就在这段短短的对话的期间，{w=.3}\n睡意已经不由分说地向我袭击而来了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1586
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_5f8ccca5:

    # "I rest my head against the back of his neck,{w=.3}\nand close my eyes."
    "我把头靠到柔一的后颈上，{w=.3}\n闭上了眼睛。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1591
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_7e625744:

    # "Juuichi-san's back is so soft and warm...{p}Wrapped up in warmth and happiness,{w=.3}\nI drift off to sleep."
    "柔一的背，{w=.3}真的是又大又温暖……\n被这种幸福的暖意给包围着，{p}我一下子就睡着了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1599
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_71d25957:

    # ju "「...[ln].」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「……西村。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1600
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_6e095645:

    # fn "「...Nnah?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「……啊嗯？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1601
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d94ac34a:

    # ju "「Are you still tired from the trip back to Minasato?{p} You were pretty fast asleep.」"
    ju "「是长途旅行的疲劳还没恢复吗？\n看你睡得好熟。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1602
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d520d177:

    # "His words snap me out of my half-asleep state."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "这句话，{w=.3}让睡眼惺忪的我马上了解现在的状况。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1603
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_a536fd64:

    # "Looking around in confusion,{w=.3}\nI recognize the familiar surroundings.{p}Grandpa's house is right in front of us."
    "连忙看了一下四周，{w=.3}已经是熟悉的田园景色，\n爷爷的家就正在眼前。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1604
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b27e9edf:

    # fn "「...How long was I out?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「……我睡了多久啊？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1605
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_856a4a11:

    # ju "「About 30 minutes, give or take.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「大概快三十分钟吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1606
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_53badd18:

    # "...Wow.{w} I'd meant to sleep for\n5 minutes to clear my head.{p}I didn't mean to sleep that long."
    "……唔哇。\n想说只睡个五分钟左右，{w=.3}让脑袋休息一下就好的说。\n没想到一不小心就睡了这么久吗。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1607
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_57482b56:

    # "My thick-headedness is formidable.{p}So is Juuichi-san's soft fur, however..."
    "真是可怕啊，我的迟钝程度。\n还有另一个更可怕的，那就是柔一既温和又柔软的兽毛……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1608
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_0dff21ab:

    # fn "「Oh, I'll be fine from here. You can put me down!{p} You've been carrying me for so long...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊，已经可以放我下来了！{p}那个，让你背着我这么久真的很不好意思……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1609
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_8a5f46be:

    # ju "「This really isn't a big deal for me.{p} Are you sure about me putting you down already?」"
    ju "「没什么，这种程度对我来说还不算什么。\n已经可以站了吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1610
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_74d5aa26:

    # fn "「I can feel my legs again, mostly.{p} I'll probably be fine!」"
    fn "「腰和脚已经不会觉得不舒服了。\n应该是可以的！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1611
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_e158bee8:

    # "Juuichi-san crouches down,\nwithout wobbling in the slightest.{p}He's as stable as ever."
    "这样啊，说完后柔一便蹲了下来。\n就连一点摇晃都没有，{w=.3}和之前一样的稳定。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1612
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_8741593a:

    # "Lowering my feet to the ground,{w=.3}\nI gingerly get off him."
    "我把脚放到地上，{w=.3}用力撑起身体离开了柔一。\n身体的状况……嗯，应该没问题。\n稍微伸展了一下，{w=.3}扭了扭腰确认没问题。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1613
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_5e84bcc4:

    # "Hm... There don't seem to be any problems.{p}I lightly stretch, and twist around to test my back."
    "嗯……应该没问题。\n稍微伸展了一下，{w=.3}扭了扭腰确认没问题。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1617
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_c25f11a9:

    # ju "「Hm,{w=.3} seems that there's nothing to worry about.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「嗯，{w=.3}看来是不需要担心了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1618
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_7999ff24:

    # "Seeing that I can move my body properly,{w=.3}\nJuuichi-san gives a nod of approval."
    "看到我能够顺利地动身子的模样，{w=.3}\n柔一便点了点头。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1619
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b4a3acf7:

    # fn "「Juuichi-san,{w=.3} thank you so much for everything.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「柔一，{w=.3}不管怎么说真的是非常感谢。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1623
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_08a6a3f5:

    # ju "「Ah,{w=.3} no problem.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「不，{w=.3}没什么。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1624
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_28c13b73:

    # "As usual,{w=.3} his response is only a few words.{p}I feel like I could never compete with him.{p}...Well,{w=.3} not in judo, at least."
    "柔一如往常，非常简短地回答。\n不知怎地有种一辈子都无法与他为敌的感觉。\n……啊不，{w=.3}不是指在柔道上。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1625
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_25fd2fb9:

    # "Even so,{w=.3} next time I go out to catch fireflies,{w=.3}\nI'll make sure to ask Grandpa for a map.{p}I never thought I'd forget something like that."
    "说起来，{w=.3}如果下次还要去找萤火虫的话，{w=.3}\n可得要好好地请爷爷画张地图才行了。\n我可没办法想像要是连这也忘了会变成怎样。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1629
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_216534a3:

    # ju "「...So,{w=.3} can I go with you tomorrow?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「……这样的话，{w=.3}我陪你去吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1630
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_b5ad05af:

    # fn "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「咦？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1631
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_59a37ad7:

    # "I tried to stop myself,{w=.3}\nBut I blurted my surprise out loud anyway.{p}...I'm doing nothing but embarrassing myself today."
    "原本只是想在内心自言自语的，{w=.3}\n看来不小心说出口了的样子。\n……该怎么说，总觉得今天好像一直在做丢脸的事。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1635
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_192344f8:

    # ju "「I'm worried about letting you\n walk around alone at night.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「我不放心让西村一个人在夜晚四处跑。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1636
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_45e808db:

    # "...That's right,{w=.3} I've been a huge pain today.{p}Going along with Juuichi-san seems like a good idea."
    "……确实啦，{w=.3}今天也因此给他造成了很多麻烦。\n不过，{w=.3}请柔一陪着一起去\n或许真的是个不错的方案。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1637
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_96b2f0c7:

    # "At the very least,{w=.3}\nit'd be much more enjoyable than going alone."
    "找地点的问题也是一个，{w=.3}而且再怎么说，\n这种事情两个人看肯定比一个人看还要有趣。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1638
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_652402c5:

    # fn "「...Would you, if it's not too much trouble?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「……那，{w=.3}可以麻烦你吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1642
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_e367b661:

    # ju "「Sure.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「啊啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1643
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_4be1484d:

    # "Unfortunately, today didn't go so well.{w=.3}\nBut, in the end, things worked out all right?"
    "今天虽然没有去成很可惜，{w=.3}\n不过结果看来倒是也挺不错的样子？"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1644
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_d5a78eae:

    # "It might be a little sudden,{w=.3} but I'll prepare\nright away for our trip tomorrow.\nIt's the least I can do."
    "虽然可能有点急，{w=.3}不过正好柔一明天也有空，\n那就决定是明天去了。\n毕竟不是一个人的事了，时间就交给柔一决定吧。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1645
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_8046f146:

    # "...It's not like I have anything\nelse to do with my free time."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "……反正我就是很闲嘛。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1649
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_2d1bbc73:

    # ju "「Make sure you dress appropriately tomorrow.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「明天要好好准备过了再去啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1650
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_62c11326:

    # fn "「I will.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「好的，我知道了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1651
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_5db66248:

    # "Umm...{w=.3} A flashlight, compass, something to drink.{p}I'll be able to last for a day if anything happens!{p}...Well, that won't happen if Juuichi-san's with me."
    "那个，{w=.3}手电筒、指南针、饮料、零食。\n这些都准备了的话就算遇难也可以活个一天了！\n……啊不，因为有柔一在所以这种事不可能啦。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1652
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_39947c2d:

    # "Ah, what about nets and containers?{p}Keeping fireflies as pets seems difficult..."
    "啊，说起来要不要带捕虫网呢？\n不过要养萤火虫好像非常困难的样子……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1653
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_ebf1ab73:

    # "I'll have a look around the shed tomorrow,{w=.3}\nand see if I can find anything useful."
    "明天在家里的储藏室找找看，{w=.3}\n如果有还可以用的捕虫网的话就带过去好了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1654
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_87a5c955:

    # ju "「Well then,{w=.3} see you tomorrow.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ju "「那么，{w=.3}明天见了。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1659
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_ea8ba342:

    # "With a wave of his hand,{w=.3}\nhe turns and starts walking\nin the direction of his house."
    "柔一轻轻举起手，{w=.3}\n转身背向朝他家的方向走去。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1661
translate chinese_simplified juuichi04_rideback_98e4e624:

    # "Catching fireflies with Juuichi-san...{w=.3}\nI'm looking forward to it."
    "和柔一一起去看萤火虫吗，{w=.3}\n总觉得好期待啊。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1681
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_f32840b5:

    # fn "「It's still the same...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「没有变化呢……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1682
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_5a60eba9:

    # "The memories I'm following are fuzzy,{p}but the scenery I remember hasn't changed.{p}I mutter this to myself."
    "虽然记忆稍微有点模糊了，{p}但是，看到这和记忆中几乎没有差别的景色，\n我还是不由自主地嘟哝出来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1683
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_b843ef0c:

    # "The building seems to be a little worn.{p}This store also hasn't changed."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "走近这已经有点年代的建筑，{p}甚至连门都和以前是一样的。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1688
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_176f8e1d:

    # fn "「Oh, hello.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「打扰了——」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1689
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_95bc7b77:

    # who "「Yes?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    who "「来了——」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1690
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_cc1156a0:

    # "The store smells a little dusty and old."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "满是灰尘的小店，这种味道还真是令人怀念。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1694
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_08918e0e:

    # "When I call into the store, no one is there.{p}Then, a tanuki pops out.{p}He looks like a mini-Kounosuke."
    "空无一人的店铺中，{p}一个好像缩小版孝之助的狸兽人\n一边说话一边走了出来。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1701
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_0d1497d2:

    # yk "「Sorry, dad's out right now.{p} Is there something you need?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「不好意思，爸爸现在在外出。{p}要买些什么吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1702
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_c66b2e6f:

    # fn "「Ah. I came to see Kounosuke.{p} Is he here right now?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊，我是来找孝之助的，他在不？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1703
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_c08b722c:

    # yk "「Big brother?{p} He went somewhere...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「找哥哥吗？哥哥他现在也出去了……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1707
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_6c193778:

    # yk "「Mom! Do you know where Kounosuke went?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「妈妈——你知道哥哥去哪了吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1711
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_ac2d5a1d:

    # harue "「Well now, I was wondering that myself.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    harue "「啊，我也不知道呢。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1712
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_eb2d9c7d:

    # yk "「Looks like one of his friends is here.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「哥哥的朋友来了」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1713
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_184e32ae:

    # harue "「Maybe he didn't leave?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    harue "「他呀，是不是又出去了？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1714
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_c4b7ef60:

    # yk "「So you don't know where he is?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「所以我才问他去哪了？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1715
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_5f5ed3d1:

    # harue "「Hmm, I'm still not so sure...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    harue "「啊，不知道呢」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1716
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_9b5c6ed3:

    # "......{p}When Yukiharu-kun goes back into the store.{p}I can hear his exchange with an older woman."
    "……{p}我就站在外面\n听着店铺里面幸春和他的妈妈来言去语地说。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1720
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_1900dd66:

    # yk "「Sorry. Hmm, where did he go...{p} I think he's probably somewhere in town.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「对不起呢。不太清楚他去哪了……{p}大概是在村子里的什么地方吧。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1721
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_a8b68a28:

    # fn "「Oh well. That's okay I guess.{p} I didn't come here for anything business related.{p} Just wanted to see if he was around.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「啊，没关系，也没有什么特别的事情。{p}只是想见见他而已。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1722
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_c49ba960:

    # yk "「Really?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「是这样啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1723
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_86330bfa:

    # fn "「By the way, you're Yukiharu-kun, aren't you?{p} You've gotten bigger!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「对了，你是幸春吧？{p}长大了呢。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1727
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_a8d5fe58:

    # yk "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「诶？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1728
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_31da0127:

    # yk "「Umm, who are you?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「那个，请问你是哪位？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1729
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_5eff18d7:

    # "Guh, he doesn't remember me..."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "唔咕……不记得我了呀……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1730
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_501268e9:

    # fn "「Hey, it's me.{p} I transferred to another school 5 years ago.{p} [fn]-onii-chan. Remember?」"
    fn "「仔细看看，是我啦，我啦。{p}5年前转学的那个，\n博行哥，想起来没？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1734
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_a56bad1f:

    # yk "「......」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「……」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1735
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_da51edcc:

    # "For a while, Yukiharu stares at me, puzzled."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "幸春君莫名其妙地盯着我的脸看，"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1739
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_09e5d166:

    # yk "「Uh, ah... were you the one who...{p} always got into trouble with my brother?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「啊，啊——经常和哥哥一起惹别人生气的那个？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1740
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_9ed134ce:

    # "Oh..."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "唔……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1741
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_cbef81a0:

    # "It seems like he remembers one thing,{p}but then I would get dragged along with Kounosuke.{p}I didn't have anything to do with it."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "虽然大致上是想起来了，{p}但是那些事情都是被孝之助连累的，我可什么都没做过……"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1742
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_97f0e8e9:

    # "Well, there's no use in testifying."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "算了，那些事就算抱怨也没辙。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1743
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_be8fb6e8:

    # fn "「Y-yeah... that [fn]-onii-chan.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「对，对啦。就是那个博行哥。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1744
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_aa6abacb:

    # yk "「I kind of remember.{p} Why are you back in Minasato?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「总算想起来了。{p}回水乡村来了？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1745
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_8bfad486:

    # fn "「I'm just here for Summer vacation.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「嗯，虽然只是暑假的这段时间」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1749
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_eeba7349:

    # yk "「Oh, that's it, then.{p} Well then, I need to get back there.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「啊啊，什么嘛……{p}那么说还是要回到那边去的啊。」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1753
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_9cc90713:

    # ko "「I'm back!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ko "「我回来了——」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1754
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_5c19b3eb:

    # "While talking to Yukiharu-kun,{p}Kounosuke seems to have come back."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "正和幸春君说话的时候，孝之助回来了。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1755
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_24b99c25:

    # "When I turn around,{p}it's just one innocent tanuki face."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "回过头一看，{p}果然在那里站着一个满脸呆相的狸兽人。"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1760
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_72e111fb:

    # yk "「Ah, you're back.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「啊，哥哥你回来啦」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1761
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_8b9b287b:

    # fn "「Welcome home.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「你回来啦——」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1766
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_3b20baae:

    # ko "「Oh, what's wrong [fn]?{p} Is there something you need?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ko "「啊？博行你来啦？有什么事吗？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1767
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_d0741e89:

    # fn "「No, I just came to drop in and visit.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「没有，只是串串门而已」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1771
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_aa34ee12:

    # ko "「Ah, is that so.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ko "「啊，是那样啊」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1775
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_0d1f50cd:

    # yk "「Hey, onii-chan!{p} I'm not the only one who has to watch the store!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「话说回来，哥哥，{p}不要总是让我看店嘛！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1779
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_18b7b671:

    # ko "「What!{p} I wouldn't make you do something like that.」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ko "「诶诶！没有让你看店啊？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1780
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_1b3da474:

    # yk "「But you just went out somewhere!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「但是你一转眼就不知道去哪了」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1784
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_efb3ec89:

    # ko "「But dad didn't catch me leaving, did he?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    ko "「因为要是被爸爸抓到那就出不去了，对吧？」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1785
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_6698d4dd:

    # yk "「I wanted to go out and play too!{p} But I promised I wouldn't!」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    yk "「我也想要出去玩！已经约好了的！」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1786
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_257c9bdb:

    # fn "「C-come on now. Calm down you two...」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    fn "「嘛，好啦好啦。你们两个都冷静点」"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1787
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_ec752f36:

    # "A fight between brothers suddenly breaks out,{p}so I rush in and try to calm things down."
    # [旧版翻译]
    "突然而来的吵架，{p}我慌慌张张的给这对兄弟拉架，"

# game/Day 4.rpy:1791
translate chinese_simplified kounosuke04_13c37bac:

    # ko "「Eh? But what needs calming down?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
